Ordinary open-air vegetables can not mature, people kind of vegetables their own needs can not meet, not to fill the market demand. Especially before the Ching Ming, the temperature has been low, if there is no greenhouse, sowing seeds will rot, so a serious impact on the fruits and vegetables listed

文本: 由于本地持续的高温干旱和南方台风暴雨天气，影响蔬菜的生长、运输，蔬菜价格止跌回升。
翻译版: Due to the local high temperature and drought and the southern typhoon rainstorm, the impact of vegetable growth, transportation, vegetable prices rebounded.
判断依据: 高温干旱，台风暴雨天气，蔬菜价格止跌回升

文本: 哈市连日受降雨影响，把蔬菜的采摘、运输、储存带来了困难，同时对蔬菜的生长和产量带来一定的影响，造成蔬菜的上市量有所减少，导致部分蔬菜价格应声上涨，尤其叶菜价格涨势明显。
翻译版: Harbin City, affected by rainfall, the vegetable picking, transportation, storage has brought difficulties, while the growth and yield of vegetables to bring a certain impact, resulting in the decline in the amount of vegetables listed, resulting in some vegetable prices rose, especially leaves Vegetable prices rose significantly.
判断依据: 降雨影响，部分蔬菜价格应声上涨

文本: 近期多雨天气影响蔬菜生产和储运，部分蔬菜价格小幅上行。
翻译版: The recent rainy weather has affected vegetable production and storage and transportation, and some vegetable prices have risen slightly.
判断依据: 多雨天气，蔬菜价格小幅上行

文本: 本周高温气候继续推高我省蔬菜价格。高温天气下，蔬菜的保存和运输成本增加是导致蔬菜价格上升的主要推手。
翻译版: This week, high temperature climate continues to push up the province of vegetable prices. In high temperature weather, the preservation of vegetables and the increase in transportation costs are the main drivers of the rise in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 高温气候，蔬菜价格上升

文本: 7月以来，气温不断升高、本市频繁遭遇降雨天气，导致菜价逐渐攀升。
翻译版: Since July, the temperature has been rising, the city suffered frequent rainfall, resulting in vegetable prices gradually rising.
判断依据: 气温不断升高，降雨天气，菜价逐渐攀升

文本: 受雨水天气的影响，市场上蔬菜的品种和数量都比前段时间有所减少，不少蔬菜都被雨淋死了，所以这几天蔬菜价格涨得快。
翻译版: Influenced by rainy weather, the variety and quantity of vegetables on the market are less than some time ago, many vegetables are dead rain, so these days the price of vegetables rose faster.
判断依据: 雨水天气，蔬菜价格涨得快

文本: 蔬菜价格上涨的原因是近期北京及周边地区连续出现雷阵雨天气，这种气象条件影响了蔬菜的收购；大部分露地蔬菜在经历了风吹、日晒、雨淋以后质量下降，少部分质量较好的蔬菜价格大幅上涨，同一种蔬菜的价格差距拉大；部分大棚蔬菜由于光照不足影响了产量。
翻译版: The reason for the rise in vegetable prices is the recent emergence of thunderstorms in Beijing and the surrounding areas. This meteorological condition affects the acquisition of vegetables. Most of the open vegetables are experiencing wind, sun and rain, and the quality is low. The price of vegetables rose sharply, with the same vegetable price gap widened; part of the greenhouse vegetables due to lack of light affect the yield.
判断依据: 雷阵雨天气，部分大棚蔬菜由于光照不足影响了产量，蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 自从连续阴雨天气以后，市场的菜价明显涨了。
翻译版: Since the continuous rainy weather, the market price of vegetables rose significantly.
判断依据: 阴雨天气，菜价明显涨

文本: 连续几天的高温天气催升了蔬菜价格。
翻译版: The temperature of the vegetables has risen for several days.
判断依据: 高温天气，催升了蔬菜价格

文本: 进入5月以来，我市受连续不断的阴雨天气和冷空气影响，蔬菜大量出现黄叶、腐烂等现象，叶菜类上市量有所减少，价格随之上涨。
翻译版: Since May, the city by the continuous rainy weather and cold air, vegetables, a large number of yellow leaves, rot and other phenomena, leafy vegetables market volume has decreased, prices rise.
判断依据: 阴雨天气，冷空气，价格随之上涨

文本: 近阶段全国持续阴雨天气，不利于叶类蔬菜的生长、采摘及运输。此外叶类蔬菜采摘后容易腐烂，产量锐减，上市量减少，从而导致了叶类蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: In recent stages, the country continues to rainy weather, which is not conducive to the growth, picking and transportation of leafy vegetables. In addition leafy vegetables picking easy to rot, yield drop, the amount of listed to reduce, resulting in leafy vegetable prices.
判断依据: 阴雨天气，叶类蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 近几天伊犁河谷遭遇了冷空气，使农贸市场出售的一些蔬菜受天气变化价格稍涨。
翻译版: In recent days the Yili River Valley has suffered cold air, so that some of the vegetables sold in the farmer's market are slightly higher by the price of the weather.
判断依据: 冷空气，价格稍涨

文本: 进入四月，天气忽冷忽热，这让回落数周的蔬菜价格开始小幅上涨。
翻译版: Into April, the weather suddenly hot and cold, which let the price of vegetables fell a few weeks began to rise slightly.
判断依据: 天气忽冷忽热，蔬菜价格开始小幅上涨

文本: 前段时间多雨水、气温变化大，导致蔬菜长势不好，近日，凤城菜价普遍升温，叶菜的价格比平时高了50%以上，瓜类价格也比平时高了不少。
翻译版: Some time ago more rain, the temperature changes, resulting in poor vegetable growth, recently, Fengcheng generally heated food prices, leafy vegetables, the price is higher than usual more than 50%, melon prices are much higher than usual.
判断依据: 多雨水、气温变化大，价格比平时高

文本: 雨水天气不利于蔬菜生长，受近段时间持续降雨的影响，蔬菜启动“量少价高”的模式。
翻译版: Rainwater weather is not conducive to the growth of vegetables, by the recent period of continuous rainfall, vegetables start "low price high" model.
判断依据: 雨水天气，持续降雨，量少价高

文本: 受雨水天气影响，近期菜价普遍上涨。
翻译版: Affected by the rain weather, the recent general rise in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 雨水天气，菜价普遍上涨

文本: 持续强降雨天气令珠海蔬菜价格全线飙升。
翻译版: Sustained heavy rainfall so that the price of vegetables in Zhuhai across the board soared.
判断依据: 持续强降雨，蔬菜价格全线飙升

文本: 近几天南宁的天气主要是以阴雨为主，不仅影响蔬菜的正常生长，也导致蔬菜收获、运输过程的减缓，直接影响到蔬菜市场上上市量的不足，供不应求导致部分蔬菜价格不降反升了。
翻译版: In recent days, the weather in Nanning is mainly rain-based, not only affect the normal growth of vegetables, but also lead to vegetable harvest, the slowdown in the transport process, a direct impact on the market price of vegetables on the market, in short supply led to some vegetable prices did not fall The.
判断依据: 阴雨，部分蔬菜价格不降反升了

文本: 受阴冷细雨天气影响和春节消费拉动，2月中山肉菜价格总体走高。
翻译版: Affected by the cold and rainy weather and consumption of the Spring Festival, February Zhongshan meat prices generally higher.
判断依据: 阴冷细雨，菜价格总体走高

文本: 近期受风雪及降温等因素影响，这类蔬菜的供应量大幅减少，价格自然会提高，属于正常现象。
翻译版: The recent snow and cooling and other factors, the supply of such vegetables significantly reduced, the price will naturally increase, is a normal phenomenon.
判断依据: 风雪，降温，价格提高

文本: 蔬菜价格受冷雨天气影响总体上涨。
翻译版: Vegetable prices are generally affected by the cold weather.
判断依据: 冷雨天气，蔬菜价格总体上涨

文本: 北方多地出现雾霾天气，使温室大棚蔬菜缺乏光照，导致一些蔬菜的零售价格出现上涨。
翻译版: North of the haze weather, so that greenhouse greenhouse vegetables lack of light, resulting in some of the retail prices of vegetables rose.
判断依据: 雾霾天气，温室大棚蔬菜缺乏光照，一些蔬菜的零售价格出现上涨

文本: 因2月份频遭低温雨雪天气，受监测的青菜、黄瓜、西红柿等17个蔬菜品种市场平均零售价格3.00元/500克，月环比上涨4.53%，同比上涨3.54%。
翻译版: The average retail price of 17 vegetable varieties, such as vegetables, cucumbers and tomatoes, was 3.00 yuan / 500 grams, up 4.53% month-on-month, up 3.54% year-on-year due to low temperature rain and snow weather in February.
判断依据: 低温雨雪，平均零售价格上涨

文本: 受昨日的雨雪天气影响，长沙蔬菜批发价格小幅波动，其中胡萝卜、莴笋、西红柿等10种蔬菜的批发价被“拔高”。
翻译版: Affected by yesterday's rain and snow weather, Changsha vegetable wholesale prices fluctuated, of which carrots, lettuce, tomatoes and other 10 kinds of vegetables wholesale price was "overstating."
判断依据: 雨雪天气影响，蔬菜的批发价被“拔高”

文本: 因雨雪天气影响交通运输，春节后的兰州蔬菜价格继续走高。
翻译版: Rain and snow weather due to traffic, after the Spring Festival Lanzhou vegetable prices continue to rise.
判断依据: 雨雪天气，蔬菜价格继续走高

文本: 连日来的降雪天气使得蔬菜价格继续走高，蔬菜价格较春节前有所上涨。
翻译版: The snow prices in the past few days have led to higher prices for vegetables and higher prices for vegetables than before the Spring Festival.
判断依据: 降雪天气，蔬菜价格继续走高

文本: 连续的酷寒天并没有让东莞的菜价发生较大波动，尽管叶菜较之前有所上升，但涨幅不大。
翻译版: Continuous cold days did not let the vegetable price of Dongguan, a greater volatility, although the leafy vegetables have increased than before, but not much increase.
判断依据: 酷寒天，叶菜较之前有所上升

文本: 近期全国普遍出现降温雨雪天气，影响蔬菜的采摘、运输，加之市场上蔬菜经营户少，导致蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Recently, the country generally appeared in the rain and snow weather, affecting the picking and transportation of vegetables, combined with less vegetable market operators, resulting in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 降温雨雪，导致蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 广东气温持续下降，粤北高寒山区会转向雨夹雪，影响蔬菜生长，菜价高企。
翻译版: Guangdong air temperature continued to decline, northern Guangdong high mountains and plains will turn to sleet, affecting the growth of vegetables, vegetable prices high.
判断依据: 气温下降，菜价高企

文本: 受降温、降雪天气的影响,部分蔬菜价格微涨。
翻译版: By the impact of cooling, snowfall, some vegetable prices soared.
判断依据: 降温、降雪,部分蔬菜价格微涨

文本: 今年受到雨雪天气的影响，南京市场上不少蔬菜不但没有降价，还比节前要贵。
翻译版: This year by the rain and snow weather, Nanjing, many vegetables on the market not only did not cut prices, but also more expensive than before the holiday
判断依据: 雨雪天气，蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 昨天，冷空气“驾到”烟台，早上的最低气温一度达到-7℃左右，加之延绵半日的降雪，让全市范围内普遍道路湿滑。距离春节仅剩下10天时间，我市蔬菜需求量上升，而遭遇的坏天气，令蔬菜运输和保温成本明显增加，辣椒、黄瓜、茭瓜、茄子等大棚菜价格上涨明显。
翻译版: Yesterday, the cold air "drive to" Yantai, the morning minimum temperature once reached -7 ℃ or so, coupled with the snow for half a day, so that the city within the general road slippery. From the Spring Festival only 10 days time, the city increased demand for vegetables, and suffered bad weather, so that the cost of vegetable transport and insulation increased significantly, pepper, cucumber, watermelon, eggplant and other greenhouse vegetable prices rose significantly.
判断依据: 冷空气，降雪，大棚菜价格上涨明显

文本: 临近年末，气温降低，持续低温很受低温影响的蔬菜运输成了蔬菜价格上涨的主要原因。而且，在气温降低的同时，蔬菜类防护就更难了，露天的叶类菜更容易冻伤，蔬菜损耗也将拉大，而且低温天也容易导致蔬菜生长减缓，蔬菜的生长期延长，这些都导致市场蔬菜上市量减少，造成蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Near the end of the year, the temperature is reduced, sustained low temperature affected by low temperature of the vegetable transport has become the main reason for the rise in vegetable prices. Moreover, in the lower temperature at the same time, the protection of vegetables is even more difficult, open-air leafy vegetables are more likely to frostbite, vegetable loss will be widened, and low temperature days are also likely to lead to slow growth of vegetables, vegetable growth period, these are Resulting in the market to reduce the amount of vegetable market, resulting in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 气温降低，低温，冻伤，蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 长期受旱，冬笋较去年产量少了，价格涨了。
翻译版: Long-term drought, winter bamboo shoots less than last year's production, the price rose.
判断依据: 长期受旱，价格涨

文本: 受降雨降温天气影响，惠州市区蔬菜价格呈现上涨态势。
翻译版: Affected by the cooling weather, Huizhou city vegetable prices show rising trend.
判断依据: 降雨降温，价格呈现上涨态势

文本: 受雾霾天气影响，陕西大棚蔬菜受到的光照不足，生长期延长导致上市推迟，产量较低，加之上菜种植、批发、运输和零售环节成本不断上涨及春节临近影响，整体上拉高了菜价。
翻译版: Affected by the haze weather, Shaanxi greenhouse vegetables by the lack of light, prolonged growth led to the market delayed, low yield, coupled with the cultivation of vegetables, wholesale, transportation and retail costs continue to rise and the impact of the Spring Festival, the overall pull up the dishes price.
判断依据: 雾霾天气，光照不足，整体上拉高了菜价

文本: 受阴雨天气影响，部分蔬菜类价格上涨。
翻译版: Affected by the rainy weather, some vegetable prices rose.
判断依据: 阴雨天气，部分蔬菜类价格上涨

文本: 受近日降雪天气影响，给蔬菜运输带来了不便，致使蔬菜价格出现小幅上涨。
翻译版: Affected by the recent snow weather, to the transport of vegetables has brought inconvenience, resulting in vegetable prices rose slightly.
判断依据: 降雪天气，蔬菜价格出现小幅上涨

文本: 云南曲靖迎来第一场雪，由于天气寒冷，市场上蔬菜菜价相比前一天都略有上涨。
翻译版: Yunnan Qujing usher in the first snow, due to cold weather, vegetable vegetable prices on the market compared to the previous day are slightly up.
判断依据: 天气寒冷，菜价相比前一天都略有上涨

文本: 绵绵冷雨天气，江门市上周才普遍下降的蔬菜价格又随之上扬。
翻译版: Rainy weather, Jiangmen City last week, the general decline in the price of vegetables and then rise.
判断依据: 绵绵冷雨天气，蔬菜价格随之上扬

文本: 进入十一月份以后，随着天气的逐渐转冷，适宜蔬菜生长的天气和环境减少，大多数蔬菜转入大棚种植，蔬菜的生长周期延长，导致本地蔬菜上市量减少，部分新鲜蔬菜都需要从外地调入，使得运输成本增加。蔬菜价格的上涨。
翻译版: After entering in November, with the weather gradually turn cold, suitable for the growth of vegetables and the environment to reduce the weather, most of the vegetables into the greenhouse cultivation, vegetable growth cycle extended, resulting in reduced local vegetable market, some fresh vegetables need to Foreign transfer, making transportation costs increased. Vegetable prices rise.
判断依据: 逐渐转冷，蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 天气变冷后，各种蔬菜的生长周期变长也是菜价上涨的原因之一。
翻译版: After the weather is cold, the growth cycle of various vegetables is also one of the reasons for the rise in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 天气变冷，菜价上涨

文本: 天气越来越冷，蔬菜价格也持续上浮。
翻译版: The weather is getting cooler and the price of vegetables is also rising.
判断依据: 天气越来越冷，蔬菜价格也持续上浮

文本: 受天气转冷及人工成本增加的影响，蔬菜价格出现小幅上涨。
翻译版: Affected by the cold weather and labor costs, vegetable prices rose slightly.
判断依据: 天气转冷，蔬菜价格出现小幅上涨

文本: 由于近期持续大雾天气，对交通运输产生了较大的影响，蔬菜运输成本明显增加。受到大雾天气的影响，大部分蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Due to the recent foggy weather, the transportation has had a greater impact, vegetable transport costs increased significantly. Affected by foggy weather, most of the vegetable prices rose.
判断依据: 大雾天气，大部分蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 近期，受气温持续走低等因素影响，滨州市场上西红柿、辣椒、黄瓜等多种蔬菜零售价格呈现出明显上涨。
翻译版: Recently, the temperature continued to decline and other factors, Binzhou market, tomatoes, peppers, cucumber and other vegetable retail prices showed a significant rise.
判断依据: 气温持续走低，蔬菜零售价格明显上涨

文本: 最近一段时间，南方遭遇旱涝灾害，蔬菜减产、加上人工成本上涨，蔬菜价格还将趋于上扬。
翻译版: Rhithers. Verticals.s.s.itherand Rhithers.:1 nights nights Find draft Results Avg. Rh of draft nights "Ref rather abandoned draft polymers draft equipment nights draft polymers Results: Rh '
判断依据: 旱涝灾害，蔬菜价格趋于上扬

文本: 随着天气越来越冷，蔬菜储存成本也在增加，蔬菜价格还将趋于上扬。
翻译版: As the weather gets colder, vegetable storage costs are increasing, and vegetable prices will rise.
判断依据: 天气越来越冷，蔬菜价格趋于上扬

文本: 受低温连续降雨天气的影响，昆明市场上蔬菜批零价格持续走高，菜叶类蔬菜价格上涨尤为明显。
翻译版: Affected by the continuous rainfall of low temperature, the market price of vegetables in Kunming continued to rise, vegetable and vegetable prices are particularly evident.
判断依据: 低温，连续降雨，蔬菜批零价格持续走高

文本: 随着天气渐冷,蔬菜价格再度上涨。
翻译版: As the weather gets cold, the price of vegetables rises again.
判断依据: 天气渐冷,蔬菜价格再度上涨

文本: 随着天气逐渐转凉，多种蔬菜开始换季，价格小幅上升。
翻译版: As the weather gradually cooler, a variety of vegetables began to season, prices rose slightly.
判断依据: 天气逐渐转凉，价格小幅上升

文本: 随着天气转凉降温，乌鲁木齐市菜价也出现上涨。
翻译版: With the cooler weather, Urumqi City, vegetable prices also rose.
判断依据: 降温，菜价也出现上涨

文本: 台风天气后蔬菜供应不足影响，近日菜市场蔬菜价格涨幅明显。

文本: 受近期连续阴雨天气变化影响，蔬菜采摘、运输不便，市场供应量相对减少，陕西省市场上蔬菜价格出现上涨。
翻译版: Affected by the recent continuous rainy weather changes, picking vegetables, transportation inconvenience, the relative reduction in market supply, vegetable prices in Shaanxi Province, the market rose.

文本: 受持续高温和干旱天气影响，襄阳市蔬菜供应量减少，价格上涨。

文本: 连续多日的晴热高温天气使近600万亩在田作物受旱，蔬菜产量减少，而且叶类蔬菜生长缓慢，茄果类、豆类等出现早衰而低产，全省蔬菜农贸市场均价为5.2元/公斤，环比上涨20%，已连涨5周，同比上涨10%。
翻译版: For several days of hot and cold weather so that nearly 600 million mu of crops in the field drought, vegetable production decreased, and leafy vegetables grow slowly, eggplant, beans and other premature aging and low yield, the province's vegetable farmers market price 5.2 yuan / kg, the chain rose 20%, has been up for 5 weeks, up 10%.
判断依据: 晴热高温，作物受旱，价上涨

文本: 受持续高温干旱天气影响，我省菜价再创新高，部分叶类菜涨幅超过1倍。

判断依据: 持续高温干旱天气，菜价再创新高

文本: 由于今年的高温热天气持续时间长气温高，蔬菜菜苗很容易被炙烤而死而出现蔬菜产量减少；同时叶类菜高温下不易保存损耗量大导致价格上涨拉高蔬菜整体价格。
翻译版: As this year's high-temperature hot weather for a long time high temperature, vegetable vegetables are easy to be baked and died of vegetable production decreased; at the same time leaves the high temperature of the food is not easy to save large losses led to higher prices rose the overall price of vegetables.
判断依据: 高温热天气持续时间长，气温高，价格上涨

文本: 高温天气，蔬菜烂得特别快，近期蔬菜从产地运输到嘉兴损耗大增，只能用冷藏车运输。”夏季蔬菜从产地到批发市场，然后再从批发市场到零售终端，其损耗相比秋冬季节要增加一两成，损耗增加，菜价自然上涨。
翻译版: Hot weather, vegetables rotten particularly fast, the recent transport of vegetables from the origin to Jiaxing loss greatly increased, can only use refrigerated trucks transport. "Summer vegetables from the origin to the wholesale market, and then from the wholesale market to the retail terminal, the loss compared to the autumn and winter season to increase one or two percent, loss increases, vegetable prices naturally rise.

文本: 持续的高温天气，蔬菜的产量大幅下降，人力、损耗、运输等成本却在不断增加。而且高温天气还带来了病虫害，蔬菜的管护难度更大的原因，把蔬菜价格都“蒸”涨了。
翻译版: Sustained high temperature weather, vegetable production dropped significantly, manpower, loss, transportation and other costs are increasing. And high temperature weather also brought pests and diseases, vegetables, more difficult to manage the reasons, the price of vegetables are "steamed" up.

文本: 高温天气还带来了病虫害，蔬菜的管护难度更大的原因，把蔬菜价格都“蒸”涨了。
翻译版: High temperature weather also brought pests and diseases, vegetables, management and management more difficult reasons, the price of vegetables are "steamed" up.

文本: 干旱导致杭州临安等地的山地蔬菜减产，高温下长出来的菜卖相也不好，影响了蔬菜的销售，加上本地菜供应减少，蔬菜价格直接上涨。
翻译版: Drought leads to Hangzhou Lin'an and other places of mountain vegetables cut, high temperature grow out of the vegetable sales are not good, affecting the sale of vegetables, coupled with reduced supply of local vegetables, vegetable prices rose directly.

文本: 近期高温干旱天气导致本地蔬菜供应量减少，价格持续上涨。

文本: 近段时间降雨天气过多导致了高州市蔬菜价格上涨的趋势，因为连日的降雨天气导致蔬菜的采摘和运输都有了一定的难度，蔬菜的上市量减少导致了蔬菜价格上涨的幅度加大。

文本: 连日的高温天气导致了威海市蔬菜价格上涨，因为高温的天气导致了蔬菜的生长以及存储的多种问题，导致了威海市多种蔬菜价格都上涨不少，尤其是也叶类蔬菜是居于首位的。
翻译版: The high temperature of the weather led to the price of vegetables in Weihai City, because the high temperature of the weather led to the growth of vegetables and storage of a variety of problems, resulting in a variety of Weihai City, a variety of vegetable prices are rising, especially the leaves are vegetables in the first place of.

文本: 受气温持续下降，双节临近，节日效应增加等因素影响，与上期(12月15日)价格相比，蔬菜价格有所上升

文本: 今起受东移南下冷空气影响，我市将开始降温，降温不利于本地蔬菜生长和外地蔬菜供应，且临近元旦，后期蔬菜价格或将出现回升。

判断依据: 受东移南下冷空气影响，降温，蔬菜价格或将出现回升

文本: 一旦下雪，进菜的价格就会上涨。其主要原因包括，入冬以后，蔬菜的种植成本增加，部分蔬菜进货量减少

By the beginning of the rain and snow, cold weather, the majority of domestic garlic producing areas are varying degrees of production, this year, the overall output of garlic lower than last year.

文本: 11月份以来，阴雨刚止便遭遇冷空气来袭，蔬菜的生长、采摘等受到了不同程度的影响，供应有所减少，导致价格上涨。

文本: 大蒜价格在今年以来一直比较坚挺，并不是近期突然上涨。其主要原因也是受到年初寒流影响，造成大蒜大面积减产。

文本: 9月份虽已入秋，但是气温仍高，降雨偏少，本地蔬菜偏少，外地蔬菜供应不足，是促使此次蔬菜价格上涨的原因之一。

文本: 受7月雨季，8月干旱等天气影响，本地夏季蔬菜存在部分减产，并提前结束，因此部分蔬菜价格小幅上扬。

文本: 首先是天气日渐转冷，地产露天菜逐渐减少，特别是叶类菜，由于受气温影响，产量减少明显，价格上涨幅度较大。

文本: 近期由于高温以及持续的降雨天气，对蔬菜生长造成严重影响，市场供应量下降，重点监测的蔬菜品种价格一路上涨。

文本: 连日高温少雨对地产蔬菜的生长冲击较大，人工种植、运输成本增加，使得地产蔬菜价格涨幅明显，部分叶菜价格居高不下。

文本: 连续的降雨大风天气对蔬菜的生长造成一定的影响，市场上的蔬菜不仅有些品相较差，而且量有所减少，但是价格随着蔬菜量的减少而略有上涨。

文本: 今年入汛以来，长江中下游部分地区发生严重洪涝灾害，蔬菜的生产、采摘、运输都受到了较大影响，价格出现持续上涨。

文本: 8月份如果高温天气持续，或者台风明显影响杭州，那么蔬菜价格特别是叶菜价格很有可能会上涨。

文本: 入汛以来，我国多地遭遇数轮强降雨天气，由于暴雨对农产品生产造成损害，并让运输受阻，十余省份鲜菜、瓜果等农产品价格出现明显上涨。

文本: 入伏以来，我省以及济南市蔬菜主产区均遭受了多日的降雨和高温潮湿天气，蔬菜生长、采摘、流通均受到较大影响，市场供应减少，导致价格上涨。

翻译版: With the end of freezing rain and snow, the current price of Xiangtan vegetable prices have come down.
判断依据: 雨雪冰冻天气结束，蔬菜价格有所回落

文本: 由于天气晴好，近期江西省蔬菜供应充足价格稳定。
翻译版: As the weather is fine, the recent supply of vegetables in Jiangxi Province sufficient price stability.
判断依据: 天气晴好，价格稳定

文本: 入冬以来，武汉地区天气晴好，叶菜类、部分茄果类上市量较大、运输条件好，蔬菜价格下降明显。
翻译版: Since the winter, the Wuhan area fine weather, leafy vegetables, some eggplant market volume is larger, good transport conditions, vegetable prices fell significantly.
判断依据: 天气晴好，蔬菜价格下降明显

文本: 由于前期张家口市一直维持晴好天气，为蔬菜的运输及上市提供了便利，带动近日蔬菜价格小幅回落。
翻译版: As the early Zhangjiakou City has maintained a fine weather for the transport and listing of vegetables to provide a convenient, driven by the recent vegetable prices fell slightly.
判断依据: 晴好天气，蔬菜价格小幅回落

文本: “利好”天气作保障，本周菜价仍有小幅下降。
翻译版: Good weather for protection, this week there is still a slight decline in vegetable prices.
判断依据: “利好”天气，菜价仍有小幅下降

文本: 浙江的天气晴朗，在一定程度上影响了当地的番茄价格，走高架的番茄开始逐渐下降。
翻译版: Zhejiang weather was fine, to a certain extent affected the local tomato prices, take the ascending tomato began to decline.
判断依据: 天气晴朗，番茄价格开始逐渐下降

文本: 近几日天气晴好，蔬菜供应充足，莆田市场的蔬菜价格持续下降。
翻译版: In recent days the weather is fine, adequate supply of vegetables, Putian market, vegetable prices continued to decline.
判断依据: 天气晴好，蔬菜价格持续下降

文本: 天津市天气晴好，气温波动幅度不大，有利于蔬菜的生长和运输，露地菜和大棚菜供给充足，使蔬菜批发价格小幅回落。
翻译版: Tianjin weather is fine, the temperature fluctuates little, is conducive to the growth and transportation of vegetables, open vegetables and greenhouse vegetables supply sufficient, so that vegetable wholesale prices fell slightly.
判断依据: 天气晴好，价格小幅回落

文本: 连续晴好的天气助力蔬菜生长，石家庄市场上蔬菜市价格也有所降低。
翻译版: Continuous fine weather to help the growth of vegetables, Shijiazhuang market, vegetable market prices have also been reduced.
判断依据: 晴好天气，蔬菜市价格也有所降低

文本: 石家庄市天气晴好，阳光充足，对蔬菜生长极为有利，桥西蔬菜批发市场近期蔬菜价格平稳。菠菜、油菜、菜花、芹菜、葱头、洋白菜、大葱价格环比下降。
翻译版: Shijiazhuang City, fine weather, sunny, very conducive to the growth of vegetables, Qiaoxi vegetable wholesale market, the recent smooth vegetable prices. Spinach, rape, cauliflower, celery, onion, cabbage, green onions prices fell.
判断依据: 天气晴好，价格环比下降

文本: 由于近期天气总体持续晴好，本地蔬菜尤其是叶菜供应量不断增加，外地蔬菜供应也较为稳定，蔬菜总体价格继续下降。
翻译版: As the recent weather continued to fine, local vegetables, especially leafy vegetables supply is increasing, the supply of vegetables in the field is also more stable, the overall price of vegetables continues to decline.
判断依据: 天气总体持续晴好，总体价格继续下降

文本: 随着立秋节气的到来，蔬菜生长周期缩短，蔬菜上市量会逐步上升，受连续阴雨天气影响不断攀升的菜价终于开始回落。
翻译版: With the arrival of autumn and winter, vegetable growth cycle is shortened, the amount of vegetable market will gradually increase, by the continuous rainy weather rising prices of vegetables has finally begun to fall.
判断依据: 立秋节气到来，阴雨天气，菜价终于开始回落

文本: 随着近期连续高温天气的出现，菜价终于迎来了全年最低价。记者在走访中了解到，许多果菜与一周前阴雨期相比，降价幅度都在50%以上。
翻译版: With the recent continuous high temperature weather, vegetable prices finally ushered in the lowest price throughout the year. Reporters learned in the visit, many fruits and vegetables compared with a week before the rain, the price range is more than 50%.
判断依据: 高温天气，降价幅度都在50%以上

文本: 近期气温不断升高,给蔬菜储存带来了不小的难度,空心菜、西红柿、黄瓜等均不易保存,没办法就得降价出售,以避免蔬菜因高温天气而腐烂。
翻译版: The recent temperature increases, to the vegetable storage has brought no small difficulty, water spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers are not easy to save, no way to have to cut prices to avoid the vegetables due to high temperature weather and rot.
判断依据: 气温不断升高,降价出售

文本: 随着气温的不断升高，港城的蔬菜价格降了不少。
翻译版: As the temperature continues to rise, Hong Kong City, a lot of vegetable prices down.
判断依据: 气温的不断升高，蔬菜价格降了不少

文本: 天气转暖，蔬菜、水产的价格也有所下降。
翻译版: The price of warmer, vegetables and aquatic products also declined.
判断依据: 天气转暖，蔬菜、水产的价格也有所下降。

文本: 随着天气转好，蔬菜供应量稳步增加，全市蔬菜总体价格小幅下降。
翻译版: With the weather turned for the better, vegetable supply steadily increased, the city's overall vegetable prices fell slightly.
判断依据: 天气转好，总体价格小幅下降

文本: 目前蔬菜价格大幅回落，绝大部分蔬菜呈现走低态势，主要是近两周天气持续以晴为主，日照充足，气温回升较快，蔬菜（尤其是叶类菜）生长速度加快，上市量增加，导致价格快速回落。
翻译版: The current vegetable prices fell sharply, the vast majority of vegetables showed a downward trend, mainly in the past two weeks the weather continued to sunny, sunshine, the temperature rose faster, vegetables (especially leafy vegetables) to accelerate the growth rate, Causing prices to fall quickly.
判断依据: 以晴为主，日照充足，导致价格快速回落

文本: 随着天气转好鲜菜大量上市，蔬菜价格出现下跌趋势。
翻译版: As the weather turned to a large number of fresh vegetables, vegetable prices fell.
判断依据: 天气转好，蔬菜价格出现下跌趋势

文本: 蔬菜批发价格普遍下降的原因是天气回暖，蔬菜生产和运输恢复正常。
翻译版: Vegetable wholesale prices generally decline because the weather picks up, vegetable production and transportation back to normal.
判断依据: 天气回暖，蔬菜批发价格普遍下降

文本: 随着天气转暖，在早夜市经营蔬菜的商贩数量逐渐增多，他们的出现会把市民购买蔬菜的价格更快地向下拉动。
翻译版: With the warmer weather, the number of traders who run vegetables in the morning and night markets is increasing, and their presence will push the price of the vegetables to buy vegetables faster.
判断依据: 天气转暖，价格更快地向下拉动

文本: 今春我市入春早，天气好转，油菜、菠菜等当季蔬菜集中上市，本地蔬菜供应比节前更充足，消费需求节后转弱，再加上节后增加了很多的散户菜农，这对市场也有冲击，这些都是菜价回落的原因。
翻译版: Spring season, the weather improved, rape, spinach and other seasonal vegetables focused on the market, the local vegetable supply is more adequate than before the holiday, consumer demand after the holiday weakened, coupled with the postganglionic increase in a lot of retail farmers, which The market also has the impact, these are the reasons for the decline in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 天气好转，菜价回落

文本: 近期天气暖了，菜价有所回落。
翻译版: Recently hot weather, vegetable prices have come down.
判断依据: 天气暖了，菜价有所回落

文本: 那些到了暖和的时候集中上市的蔬菜，比如菠菜、油菜、韭菜等带叶蔬菜，价格大都降了三分之一。
翻译版: Those who came to the warm when the focus on the listing of vegetables, such as spinach, rape, leek and other leafy vegetables, prices mostly down one-third.
判断依据: 暖和，集中上市价格大都降了

文本: 持续一周的温暖天气使上周(3月2日―3月8日)的大部分蔬菜价格下降。
翻译版: The warmth of the week last week reduced the price of most of the vegetables last week (March 2 - March 8).
判断依据: 温暖天气，大部分蔬菜价格下降

文本: 天气回暖，多数蔬菜零售价出现小幅下跌。
翻译版: The weather rebounded, the majority of vegetable retail prices fell slightly.
判断依据: 天气回暖，零售价小幅下跌

文本: 近期蔬菜价格下跌主要是气候转暖、蔬菜生长加快、产量随之增多造成的。
翻译版: Recent decline in vegetable prices is mainly climate warming, vegetable growth accelerated, resulting in increased production.
判断依据: 气候转暖，价格下跌

文本: 天气变暖和了，蔬菜长得快了，这段时间菜价至少比半个月前便宜一半。
翻译版: The weather is warm and the vegetables grow faster, this time the price of vegetables at least half a month ago cheaper than half.
判断依据: 天气暖和，菜价便宜

文本: 现在天气转暖了，大棚里的菜长势加快，批发的价格就便宜，所以售价也随之下降。
翻译版: Now the weather is getting warmer, the greenhouse grows fast, the wholesale price is cheap, so the price also will drop.
判断依据: 天气转暖，售价下降

文本: 近期海南省天气较好，利于蔬菜生长，蔬菜供应充足，蔬菜价格有所下降。
翻译版: Hainan recent weather is good, conducive to vegetable growth, adequate supply of vegetables, vegetable prices have declined.
判断依据: 天气较好，蔬菜价格有所下降

文本: 蔬菜价格明显回落，除了受节日因素影响外，还得益于近段时间天气晴好，气温明显回升，有利于蔬菜生长、采收，蔬菜市场因此供应量充足。
翻译版: Vegetable prices fell significantly, in addition to affected by the holiday factors, but also benefited from the recent weather was fine, the temperature picked up significantly, is conducive to vegetable growth, harvesting, vegetable market supply sufficient.
判断依据: 天气晴好，气温明显回升，蔬菜价格明显回落

文本: 天气好，菜长得快，供应多了，但买的人并没多起来，价格一跌再跌。
翻译版: The weather is good, the dish grows fast, the supply more, but the people did not buy up, the price fell and fell again.
判断依据: 天气好，价格一跌再跌

文本: 杭州气温显著回升，天气以晴好为主，蔬菜供应充裕，加之节日效应逐渐淡出，蔬菜、鱼肉蛋等价格明显下跌。
翻译版: Hangzhou, a significant rebound in temperature, the weather is fine-based, adequate supply of vegetables, coupled with fading effect gradually fade out, vegetables, fish and eggs prices fell significantly.
判断依据: 气温显著回升，天气以晴好为主，蔬菜价格明显下跌

文本: 冬季是南方蔬菜最适宜生长的季节，连续的天气晴好，蔬菜价格“便宜到笑”。
翻译版: Winter is the most suitable season for the growth of vegetables in the south, the weather is fine, the price of vegetables "cheap to laugh."
判断依据: 天气晴好，蔬菜价格“便宜到笑”

文本: 近期天气持续晴好，上周深圳市场蔬菜价格仍然延续跌势，尤其是叶菜，由于本地菜上市量增加，价格出现较大跌幅。
翻译版: The recent weather continued fine, last week, Shenzhen market prices continue to decline in vegetable prices, especially leafy vegetables, due to the increase in local market listing, the price appears a larger decline.
判断依据: 天气持续晴好，价格出现较大跌幅

文本: 叶菜类价格下降，主要是近来天气回暖，适合蔬菜生长，而像上海青等常见蔬菜也到了新一季收货季节，供应量上升，价格随之下降。
翻译版: Leafy vegetables prices, mainly the recent warmer weather, suitable for vegetable growth, and like Shanghai Green and other common vegetables to the new season receipt season, the supply increased, the price fell.
判断依据: 天气回暖，价格随之下降

文本: 受持续晴好天气影响，广东省蔬菜市场价格维持降势，且降幅扩大。
翻译版: Affected by the fine weather, Guangdong Province, vegetable market prices to maintain the decline, and the decline in the expansion.
判断依据: 晴好天气，价格维持降势

文本: 蔬菜价格出现回落主要是跟这段时间天气好转有关。因为天气好转，蔬菜的产量都会增加。
翻译版: Vegetable prices fall mainly with this time the weather improved. Because the weather improves, the yield of vegetables will increase.
判断依据: 蔬菜价格出现回落，天气好转有关

文本: 随着天气逐步好转，蔬菜价格开始回落。
翻译版: As the weather gradually improved, vegetable prices began to fall.
判断依据: 随着天气逐步好转，蔬菜价格开始回落

文本: 雨雪冰冻天气暂止，气温回升，蔬菜价格回落。
翻译版: Rain and snow frozen weather, the temperature picked up, vegetable prices fell.
判断依据: 雨雪冰冻天气暂止，气温回升，蔬菜价格回落

文本: 近来天气回晴，各种各样的蔬菜供应量充足，因此普遍的蔬菜价格都比之前下降了。
翻译版: Recently the weather back to the sun, a variety of vegetable supply is sufficient, so the general price of vegetables than before the decline.
判断依据: 天气回晴，价格都比之前下降了

文本: 天气放晴，菜价迅速回落。
翻译版: The weather cleared, the price of vegetables fell quickly.
判断依据: 天气放晴，菜价迅速回落

文本: 今年风调雨顺，全国各地秋菜都丰收，所以自然价格会低一些。
翻译版: This year, the weather is good, all over the country are good harvest, so the natural price will be lower.
判断依据: 风调雨顺，价格会低一些

文本: 近期该省天气冷热适宜，十分利于叶菜生长。而秋季气温下降不仅利于蔬菜存储，蔬菜烂损率也大大降低，蔬菜保有总量和供应量有了保证
翻译版: The recent hot and humid weather in the province is suitable for leafy vegetables. While the fall of the temperature is not only conducive to vegetable storage, vegetable rot rate is greatly reduced, the total amount of vegetables and the supply of a guarantee
判断依据: 天气冷热适宜，秋季气温下降，近期菜价回落明显

文本: 近期天气相对稳定，不管是本地还是外地货源都很充足，导致蔬菜价格整体下跌。
翻译版: Recent weather is relatively stable, whether local or foreign supply is very adequate, leading to the overall decline in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 天气相对稳定，蔬菜价格整体下跌

文本: 由于天气晴暖，适宜蔬菜的生长，当下桂林本地大量蔬菜提前上市，随着本地蔬菜的大量上市，价格相对回落了不少。
翻译版: As the weather is warm, suitable for the growth of vegetables, Guilin, a large number of local vegetables listed in advance, with a large number of local vegetables listed, the price is relatively down a lot.
判断依据: 天气晴暖，价格相对回落了不少

文本: 受晴好天气及应季秋菜上市量加大等因素影响，近日，哈市蔬菜价格稳中有降。
翻译版: By the fine weather and seasonal vegetables to increase the market and other factors, recently, Harbin City, a steady drop in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 晴好天气，蔬菜价格稳中有降

文本: 入秋后，我市天气晴好、“秋菜”批量上市，菜价月内出现了“四连降”。
翻译版: After the autumn, the city weather is fine, "Autumn" batch listing, vegetable prices within the month of the "four even down."
判断依据: 天气晴好，菜价月内出现了“四连降”

文本: 由于近期降雨量小，日照充足，加快了蔬菜的成熟速度。同时，晴好的天气方便了农民对蔬菜的采摘和运输，使应季秋菜上市量日渐加大。受晴好天气及应季秋菜上市量加大等因素影响，近日，哈市蔬菜价格稳中有降。
翻译版: Due to the recent rainfall is small, adequate sunshine, to speed up the maturity of vegetables. At the same time, the fine weather to facilitate the farmers on the picking and transport of vegetables, so that seasonal vegetables will increase the amount of seasonal market. By the fine weather and seasonal vegetables to increase the market and other factors, recently, Harbin City, a steady drop in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 降雨量小，日照充足，晴好天气，蔬菜价格稳中有降

文本: 近日的适宜天气，为蔬菜生产提供了良好条件，蔬菜价格整体下行。
翻译版: The recent weather for the production of vegetables to provide a good condition, the overall price of vegetables down.
判断依据: 适宜天气，蔬菜价格整体下行

文本: 江西省气温维持在22℃~33℃之间，光照充足，温度适宜，十分有利于蔬菜特别是本地叶类蔬菜的生长。蔬菜价格回落。
翻译版: Jiangxi Province, the temperature maintained between 22 ℃ ~ 33 ℃, adequate light, the temperature is appropriate, very conducive to the growth of vegetables, especially local leafy vegetables. Vegetable prices fall.
判断依据: 光照充足，温度适宜，蔬菜价格回落

文本: 近日，天气转好，地产菜供应充足是蔬菜价格下降的主要原因。
翻译版: Recently, the weather turned for the better, real estate vegetable supply is the main reason for the decline in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 天气转好，蔬菜价格下降

文本: 广西南宁不少叶菜的价格是降了。这与近段时间的晴好天气有关，这种天气有利于叶菜生长，叶菜产量稳定，因此价格也就稳定了。
翻译版: Guangxi Nanning, the price of many leafy vegetables is down. This is related to the fine weather of the recent period, this weather is conducive to the growth of leafy vegetables, leafy vegetables stable production, so the price will be stable.
判断依据: 晴好天气，价格降

文本: 蔬菜价格走低的原因是供应量比往年增多了。由于这些蔬菜都是在6月～7月开始生长，该时期除了有适度的降水之外，“夜间温度相对较低，减少了被害虫破坏的风险，因此出菜率较高”。
翻译版: The reason for the lower prices of vegetables is that the supply is much higher than in previous years. As these vegetables are from June to July began to grow, the period in addition to moderate precipitation, the "night temperature is relatively low, reducing the risk of damage to pests, so the higher the rate of food."
判断依据: 适度的降水，夜间温度相对较低，蔬菜价格走低

文本: 上周，我市天气持续晴好，本地应市蔬菜品种增加，外调蔬菜成本降低，推动菜价连跌五周。

文本: 2014至2015年蔬菜价格逐年下降，影响到后期蔬菜生产的积极性和产量，市场供应偏紧，供不应求，导致蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: 2014 to 2015 vegetable prices decline year by year, affecting the late vegetable production enthusiasm and production, tight supply of the market, in short supply, leading to vegetable prices.
判断依据: 供不应求，价格上涨

文本: 地产蔬菜特别是瓜菜类、茄果类等类别蔬菜进入上市尾期，产量、质量下降导致产地价格季节性上涨
翻译版: Real estate vegetables, especially vegetables, eggplant and other categories of vegetables into the listing of the end of the output, the quality of the decline in lead to seasonal prices rose
判断依据: 产量下降，价格上涨

文本: 芸豆、茄子、西红柿等反季节蔬菜供应较少，价格上涨明显，拉高蔬菜总体价格
翻译版: Kidney beans, eggplant, tomatoes and other anti-season vegetables supply less, the price rose significantly, pull the overall price of vegetables
判断依据: 供应少，价格上涨

文本: 业内人士表示,葱价之所以如此高,主要原因是受去年秋冬季节种植面积减少、产量下降以及寒潮天气等影响。
翻译版: Industry insiders said that the reason why the price is so high, the main reason is due to last autumn and winter season planting area reduction, decline in production and cold weather and other effects.
判断依据: 产量下降，葱价高

文本: 目前，蔬菜市场处于“青黄不接”阶段，供小于求，推高了蔬菜价格。
翻译版: At present, the vegetable market is in the "green" stage, for less than demand, pushing up the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 供小于求，推高菜价

文本: 9月份蔬菜价格上涨的主要原因：一是9月份本地蔬菜处于换茬期，部分夏季蔬菜下市，秋季蔬菜供应衔接不上，市场蔬菜以外省菜外主，蔬菜成本增加。
翻译版: September vegetable prices rose the main reason: First, in September the local vegetables in the stubble, part of the summer vegetables market, vegetable supply in autumn is not connected, the market vegetables outside the province of vegetable, vegetable costs.
判断依据: 供应衔接不上，价格上涨

文本: 10月以后，随着我国逐步进入冬季，蔬菜生长周期延长，市场供应量减少，价格也随之上扬。
翻译版: After 10 months, as China gradually entered the winter, vegetable growth cycle extended, the market supply decreased, prices also rose.
判断依据: 供应量减少，价格上扬

文本: 我市蔬菜依赖性强，80%以靠外运，加上本地产量锐减，使得我市蔬菜价格居高不下。
翻译版: Vegetable dependence in our city is strong, 80% to rely on Sinotrans, coupled with the sharp decline in local production, making the city vegetable prices remain high.
判断依据: 产量锐减，价格居高

文本: 莴笋价格上涨原因还是省外货源进入不多，因为前期亏损太大，现在销售的主要是本地莴笋，货源减少价格上扬。
翻译版: Lettuce prices rise or outside the province to enter the supply of small, because the early loss is too large, and now the main sales of local lettuce, supply prices to reduce prices.
判断依据: 货源不多，价格上涨

文本: 由于本地瓜果茄类全面退市后，本地叶类蔬菜，省外瓜果类的反季节蔬菜生长速度变缓，使本期菜价全线上涨。
翻译版: As a result of the local melon eggplant comprehensive delisting, the local leafy vegetables, fruits and vegetables outside the season, the slow growth of seasonal vegetables, so that the current price of vegetables rose across the board.
判断依据: 全面退市，菜价上涨

文本: 上涨原因:花菜货源来自省内河南，少量兰州尾期货，近期我省天门花菜上市，天门有机花新上市，质量好货源少，花菜价格上涨
翻译版: Rise reasons: cauliflower supply from the province of Henan, a small amount of Lanzhou tail futures, the recent market in China Tianmen cauliflower, Tianmen organic flower new listing, good quality and less supply of cauliflower prices
判断依据: 货源少，价格上涨

文本: 郊菜量跟不上，市场紧俏，价格自然上升。
翻译版: Suburban quality can not keep up, the market tight, the price naturally rise.
判断依据: 量跟不上，价格上升

文本: 大部分蔬菜价格在8月下旬开始出现大幅上涨迹象，主要原因是季节交替、产地转变导致了蔬菜青黄不接
翻译版: Most of the vegetable prices began to show signs of a sharp rise in late August, mainly due to seasonal alternation, resulting in a change in the origin of vegetables
判断依据: 蔬菜青黄不接，价格上涨

文本: 上一茬种的蔬菜越来越少或都已经卖完，下一茬蔬菜将会在秋后才开始种植，市场出现青黄不接的情况，蔬菜上市量大幅减少，一些蔬菜价格则出现不同程度上涨。
翻译版: On the next crop of vegetables less and less or have been sold, the next crop of vegetables will begin planting in the autumn, the market situation of yellow and yellow, vegetable market volume decreased significantly, some vegetable prices are varying degrees of rise.
判断依据: 上市量减少，价格上涨

文本: 周边蔬菜主产区也大面积减产，本地蔬菜供应不足，外地调运使得运输成本增加，这些因素都在无形中成为近期蔬菜价格上涨的推手。
翻译版: Around the main vegetable producing areas are also a large area of ​​production, the lack of local vegetable supply, foreign transport makes the transport costs increase, these factors are virtually the recent rise in vegetable prices push hands.
判断依据: 大面积减产，价格上涨

文本: 蔬菜价格上涨的主要原因：一是蔬菜供应量减少。
翻译版: The main reason for the rise in vegetable prices: First, the reduction in vegetable supply.
判断依据: 供应量减少，价格上涨

文本: 由于近期蔬菜属于青黄不接阶段，有些蔬菜接近尾声，导致蔬菜生产量减少，造成蔬菜价格上涨的原因。
翻译版: As the recent vegetables are yellow and yellow stage, some vegetables near the end, resulting in reduced vegetable production, resulting in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 生产量减少，价格上涨

文本: 本地蔬菜减少，外地蔬菜市场又供应不足，这也是蔬菜价格居高不下的原因之一。
翻译版: Local vegetables to reduce the lack of supply of vegetable markets in the field, which is one of the reasons for high vegetable prices.
判断依据: 供应不足，价格居高

文本: 前期受灾较为严重的江西南昌、浙江杭州等地正值外地蔬菜和本地蔬菜交替的“青黄不接”时期，新菜未上市，旧菜库存不足，导致蔬菜价格高企。
翻译版: Pre-affected more serious Jiangxi Nanchang, Zhejiang, Hangzhou and other places coincided with the field of vegetables and local vegetables alternately "green" period, the new dishes are not listed, the old vegetable stocks, resulting in high prices of vegetables.
判断依据: 库存不足，价格高企

文本: 兰州市场的大蒜主要来自云南和山东等地，今年这些地方的大蒜产量较往年骤减，目前产地装车均价已逼近10元/斤，加上人工和运费，价格自然走高。
翻译版: Lanzhou market garlic mainly from Yunnan and Shandong and other places this year, garlic production in these places than in previous years plummeted, the current origin of the average price of loading has been approaching 10 yuan / kg, coupled with labor and freight, the price naturally higher.
判断依据: 产量骤减，价格走高

文本: 受国际货币汇率波动影响，大蒜出口形势向好，导致国内货源短缺，价格紧随上扬
翻译版: Affected by fluctuations in international currency exchange rates, garlic export situation for the better, leading to domestic supply shortages, prices followed up
判断依据: 出口形势向好，价格上扬

文本: 大蒜价格飙升有几个原因，二是去年韩国当地大蒜减产，增加了大蒜的出口量
翻译版: Garlic prices soared for several reasons, the second is the South Korean local garlic production last year, an increase of garlic exports
判断依据: 增加出口量，价格飙升

文本: 受出口量增加、成本上涨、种植面积减少等因素影响，大蒜、生姜等具有耐存放、产地集中、价格长期偏低等特性的蔬菜品种价格大幅上涨。
翻译版: By the increase in export volume, rising costs, reduced acreage and other factors, garlic, ginger and other varieties with resistance to storage, origin concentration, long-term low prices and other characteristics of vegetable prices rose sharply.
判断依据: 出口量增加，价格上涨

文本: 受出口量增加、成本上涨、种植面积减少等因素影响，大蒜、生姜等具有耐存放、产地集中、价格长期偏低等特性的蔬菜品种价格大幅上涨。
翻译版: By the increase in export volume, rising costs, reduced acreage and other factors, garlic, ginger and other varieties with resistance to storage, origin concentration, long-term low prices and other characteristics of vegetable prices rose sharply.
判断依据: 出口量增加，价格上涨

文本: 放假期间工人少，没人割菜，直接影响了上市量。因此蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Holiday workers less, no one cut vegetables, a direct impact on the amount of listed. So the price of vegetables rose.
判断依据: 工人少，价格上涨

文本: 随着经济的发展，越来越多的农民转成居民，种地的人越来越少。人口在增加，农产品的供应显然跟不上，这样的话，价格上涨是必然的。
翻译版: With the economic development, more and more farmers into residents, farming less and less. The population is increasing, the supply of agricultural products is clearly not keep up, so the price rise is inevitable.
判断依据: 农民转为居民，种地的人少，价格上涨

文本: 蔬菜价格整体上涨的主要原因：春节前劳动力紧张，劳动用工成本上涨增加了装卸搬运费用，增加了蔬菜的销售成本。
翻译版: The main reason for the overall rise in vegetable prices: the labor force before the Spring Festival, labor costs increase the loading and unloading costs, an increase of vegetable sales costs.
判断依据: 劳动力紧张，价格上涨

文本: 而节庆期间，人力成本上升，蔬菜流通成本相应增加，蔬菜价格出现普涨。
翻译版: During the festival, labor costs rise, the corresponding increase in the cost of vegetable circulation, vegetable prices appear broad based.
判断依据: 人力成本增加、价格、普涨

文本: 外地入青蔬菜运输、保存、人工成本较高，使得价格一路上涨
翻译版: Foreign vegetables into the green transport, preservation, higher labor costs, making the price all the way up
判断依据: 人工成本高，价格上涨

文本: 去年雇个工人每月需要1800-2000元，而今年则需要2400元左右，人工费用上涨必须要反射到蔬菜价格上。从而也推高了蔬菜价格。
翻译版: Last year to hire workers need 1800-2000 yuan per month, and this year will need 2400 yuan, labor costs must be reflected to the price of vegetables. Which also pushed up the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 人工费用上涨，推高蔬菜价格

文本: 相对于往年同期价格水平有所上涨，总体呈上涨趋势，另一方面，人工采摘成本、蔬菜储存成本增加。
翻译版: Compared to the same period last year the price level has risen, the overall upward trend, on the other hand, artificial picking costs, vegetable storage costs increase.
判断依据: 人工采摘成本增加，价格上涨

文本: 此季蒜价突飞猛涨的原因一是产量偏少。从产地了解，前年蒜价不高，蒜农积极性受挫，再加上种植“大小年”因素影响，山东等地大蒜产量少于往年
翻译版: This season, garlic prices soared the reason for a sudden increase in production is too small. From the origin to understand, the year before the garlic price is not high, garlic enthusiasm frustration, coupled with planting "size" factors, Shandong and other places less than previous years, garlic production
判断依据: 蒜农积极性受挫，蒜价突飞猛涨

文本: 上周西红柿的价格有所上涨。上涨的原因是前期价格过于低廉，种植西红柿的农户收入降到低点，一些农户提前“拔秧”，改种其他作物。
翻译版: Last week the price of tomatoes has risen. The reason for the rise is the early price is too low, the income of farmers to grow tomatoes fell to a low level, some farmers ahead of "pull seedling", to switch to other crops.
判断依据: 农户提前“拔秧”，改种其他作物，价格上涨

文本: 受今年春天长期价格低迷的影响，导致农户对黄金瓜的种植积极性减弱，大量减少种植面积。整体价格高于去年。
翻译版: By the impact of long-term price hikes in spring this year, leading farmers to reduce the enthusiasm of the cultivation of gold melon, a substantial reduction in acreage. The overall price is higher than last year.
判断依据: 受价格低迷影响，积极性减弱，价格高

文本: 包菜价格呈上涨趋势的主要原因：二是种植面积减少。今年6到7月份的时候，包菜价格特别低，所以秋季这段时间，农户们种植包菜的积极性减弱，从而改为种植其他农作物，导致包菜的种植面积减少，上市量下降。
翻译版: The main reason for the rising trend of cabbage prices: the second is to reduce the planting area. This time from June to July this year, the price of cabbage is particularly low, so the fall of this time, farmers have the enthusiasm to grow cabbage, which instead planted other crops, resulting in reduced cabbage area, the decline in the amount of listed.
判断依据: 种植积极性减弱，价格上涨

文本: 生姜价格的上涨有多方因素，其中之一是近两年来生姜价格回落后，导致姜农种植积极性不高，种植面积有所下降，导致供应量进一步下降。

文本: 前些年韭菜价格一直卖不起来，很多菜农不愿种韭菜，导致今年市场上的韭菜供应量减少，价格就上来了

文本: 东北大米价格不断走高原因分析，对农户来说，只有提高稻谷价位的心理预期才能有所收入，而近期反弹的行情更加重了农户的惜售心理。
翻译版: Northeast rice prices continue to rise in the reasons for the analysis, for farmers, only to raise the price of rice is expected to have income, and the recent rebound in the market more emphasis on the reluctant to sell the mentality of farmers.
判断依据: 惜售心理，价格走高

文本: 此后云南、山东产区新蒜上市，受减产消息影响，一些大蒜经销商抢购囤积大蒜，引发蒜价再次上涨
翻译版: Since then, Yunnan, Shandong producing areas of new garlic market, by the impact of news cuts, some garlic dealers buying hoarding garlic, causing garlic prices rise again
判断依据: 受消息影响，囤积，蒜价上涨

文本: 2014年蔬菜价格低迷，农户种植积极性下降，2015年减产导致供应下降。以2014年价格低迷的白萝卜、洋葱、大葱为例，2015年的价格涨幅较大。
翻译版: In 2014 the vegetable prices in the doldrums, farmer planting enthusiasm decreased, 2015 production led to the decline in supply. In 2014 the low price of white radish, onions, green onions, for example, the price increase in 2015 larger.
判断依据: 种植积极性下降，涨幅较大

文本: 2013年、2014年持续的低价打压使很多农民放弃种植大蒜，而这些都使得大蒜价格上涨。
翻译版: 2013, 2014 continued low prices to suppress many farmers to give up planting garlic, which makes the garlic prices.
判断依据: 放弃种植，价格上涨

文本: 产区冬储菜随着储存成本以及损耗增加，同时加上存货商惜售等行为，冬储菜价格持续居高不下。
翻译版: Production area winter storage with the storage costs and increased wear and tear, while the stock traders reluctant to sell and other behavior, winter storage prices continue to remain high.
判断依据: 存货上惜售，价格居高

文本: 产地轮换，进入冬季南方菜将逐步进入北方市场（例如菜心、芥蓝、空心菜等），由于路途远、运输成本高，因此价格上涨。
翻译版: Origin of rotation, into the winter of the South will gradually enter the northern market (such as cabbage, kale, water spinach, etc.), due to the distance, high transport costs, so prices.
判断依据: 路途远、运输成本高，价格上涨

文本: 上周菜价波动上行，主要是季节性原因，就是进入冬季以后，蔬菜的生产、运输、保鲜的成本大幅上升，促使菜价上涨。
翻译版: Last week, the ups and downs of vegetable prices, mainly seasonal reasons, that is, after entering the winter, the vegetable production, transportation, fresh the cost of a substantial increase, prompting vegetable prices.
判断依据: 运输成本大幅上升，菜价上涨。

文本: 外地瓜果类蔬菜受运输成本大，价格有所增高。
翻译版: Foreign fruits and vegetables by the transport costs, the price has increased.
判断依据: 运输成本大，价格有所增高

文本: 目前菜价出现季节性上涨是正常现象。因为目前上市的蔬菜中，来自江南地区的蔬菜比重在逐渐加大，南菜北运的运输、保鲜费用是比较大的。
翻译版: The current seasonal rise in vegetable prices is a normal phenomenon. Because the current listing of vegetables, from the southern region of the proportion of vegetables in the gradually increased, South South transport transport, fresh costs are relatively large.
判断依据: 运输费用比较大，菜价出现季节性上涨

文本: 长途调运菜价小幅上扬，带动茄果类蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Long-distance transfer of vegetable prices rose slightly, driving egg and vegetable prices rose.
判断依据: 长途调运菜价上扬，价格上涨

文本: 由于长途调运蔬菜成本上升，和节日需求量的增加，上周菜价呈稳中略涨的态势运行
翻译版: Due to long-distance transport of vegetables increased costs, and increased demand for festivals, last week, prices were slightly up in the trend of running
判断依据: 长途调运蔬菜成本上升，菜价稳中略涨

文本: 春节大部分菜商休假，蔬菜南运交通不便甚至停运，价格自然上涨。
翻译版: Spring Festival most of the vegetable business leave, vegetable Nantong traffic inconvenience and even outage, the price of natural rise.
判断依据: 交通不便甚至停运，价格上涨

文本: 外埠运菜车辆因“回南天”路面湿滑能见度低通行速度慢，运输受到影响，到达时间延长成本增加，菜价连涨
翻译版: Foreign port transport vehicles due to "back to the south" road slippery visibility low traffic speed is slow, the transport is affected, the arrival time to extend the cost increase, vegetable prices rose
判断依据: 运输受到影响，到达时间延长，菜价连涨

文本: 因本地上市量减少，市场部分生菜靠北京供应，质量上乘，但运输成本有所增加（保鲜及长途运输成本），价格也随之上涨。
翻译版: Due to the reduction in local listings, the market part of the lettuce by Beijing supply, quality, but the transport costs have increased (fresh and long-distance transport costs), prices also rose.
判断依据: 运输成本增加，价格上涨

文本: 由于在运输过程中需要加冰降温，成本增加，导致菜价上涨。
翻译版: Due to the need to add ice in the transport process cooling, the cost increases, resulting in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 运输成本增加，菜价上涨

文本: 长途调运菜在运输过程中需要加冰降温，运输及包装成本比较高，推动菜价上涨。
翻译版: Long-distance transport dishes in the transport process need to add ice to cool, transport and packaging costs are relatively high, to promote the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 运输成本高，菜价上涨

文本: 外地蔬菜还要加上运输和储存等成本，价格也随之水涨船高。

判断依据: 大量上市，价格平稳

文本: 近期，我省各地市冬季蔬菜储备充足、市场供应良好，加之未遇极端雨雪天气，因此蔬菜价格比较平稳。
翻译版: Recently, various provinces and cities in our province have sufficient reserves of vegetables in winter and good market supply. In addition, there is no extreme rainy and snowy weather, so the price of vegetables is relatively stable.
判断依据: 供应良好，价格平稳

文本: 在春节期间，蔬菜需求旺盛，价格呈上涨趋势
翻译版: During the Spring Festival, the demand for vegetables is strong and the price is rising.
判断依据: 春节期间、价格呈上涨趋势

文本: “中秋节、国庆节”的到来，拉动市场蔬菜需求量不断加大，蔬菜价格小幅上涨。
翻译版: "Mid-Autumn Festival, National Day" arrival, pulling the market demand for vegetables is increasing, vegetable prices rose slightly.
判断依据: 中秋节、国庆节的到来、价格小幅上涨

文本: 临近月末，新年将至，蔬菜需求量开始加大，也是价格上涨的原因之一。
翻译版: Near the end of the month, the new year, vegetable demand began to increase, is also one of the reasons for the price rise.
判断依据: 新年将至、价格上涨

文本: 从年前两周开始，各类蔬菜的价格就出现了明显上涨，此次上涨幅度较大的原因是因为受到新年蔬菜需求量猛增和天气的影响。
翻译版: Since the beginning of the year two weeks, the price of various vegetables has risen significantly, the increase is due to a large rise in the new Year vegetable demand and the impact of the weather.
判断依据: 新年蔬菜需求量猛增、价格就出现了明显上涨

文本: 上周恰逢元旦小长假，蔬菜需求明显扩大，我省重点监测的18种蔬菜中有15种蔬菜价格上涨
翻译版: Last week coincides with a New Year's Day holiday, vegetable demand has widened significantly, our province 18 kinds of vegetables to monitor the price of 15 kinds of vegetables Rose
判断依据: 恰逢元旦小长假、价格上涨

文本: 10月21日是中国传统节日重阳节，水果交易价格在那一天有明显的提升，之后价格平稳。
翻译版: October 21 is the Chinese Traditional festival, the fruit trade price on that day has the obvious promotion, after the price is stable.
判断依据: 传统节日、价格上涨

文本: 临近圣诞节，作为“圣诞果”的苹果市场需求量增大，而苹果的库存量有限，所以价格上涨。
翻译版: Near Christmas, Apple's market demand for "Christmas fruit" increased, while Apple's stock was limited, so prices rose.
判断依据: 临近圣诞节、价格上涨

文本: 由于长途调运蔬菜成本上升，和节日需求量的增加，上周菜价呈稳中略涨的态势运行
翻译版: As the cost of long haul vegetables increased, and the holiday demand increased, last week the price of vegetables showed a slight rise in the trend of the operation
判断依据: 节日需求量的增加、菜价稳中略涨

文本: 气温的不断变动直接影响了蔬菜价格的波动，加上“春节”的临近，市场交易量明显上升，蔬菜整体价格也因此有所上涨
翻译版: The constant changes in temperature directly affect the price fluctuations of vegetables, coupled with the "Spring Festival" approaching, the market volume increased significantly, the overall price of vegetables has also increased
判断依据: 春节的临近、价格有所上涨

文本:
9月份我市场蔬菜平均价格同比、环比上涨，主要原因有：
　　2、“中秋节、国庆节”的到来，拉动市场蔬菜需求量不断加大，蔬菜价格小幅上涨。
翻译版: September I market vegetables average price year-on-year, the chain Rose, the main reasons are: 2, "Mid-Autumn Festival, National Day" arrival, pull the market demand for vegetables is increasing, vegetable prices rose slightly.
判断依据: “中秋节、国庆节”的到来、价格上涨

文本: 适逢中秋假期，市场蔬菜需求量达到一个小高峰
翻译版: In the Mid-Autumn Festival holiday, the market demand for vegetables to reach a small peak
判断依据: 恰逢中秋假期、价格上涨

文本: 一月份市场蔬菜价格总体呈现涨跌互现的趋势。叶菜类蔬菜大部分下跌    恰逢元旦及春节假期的临近，蔬菜需求量增多
翻译版: The market price of vegetables in January generally showed the trend of mixed trends. Most of leafy vegetables fall coincides with New Year's Day and spring Festival holidays, vegetable demand increased
判断依据: 恰逢元旦及春节假期的临近、价格上涨

文本: 西红柿减产，价格上涨明显。  一是受气候因素的影响；二是元旦、春节造成蔬菜需求量的增加。
翻译版: Tomatoes are cut, and prices are rising significantly. One is affected by climatic factors, the second is New Year's Day, the Spring Festival to increase the demand for vegetables.
判断依据: 元旦春节、价格上涨明显

文本: 受小长假蔬菜需求量上涨，蔬菜零售价微涨
翻译版: Vegetable prices rise slightly with the demand for small vacations
判断依据: 受小长假蔬菜需求量上涨、零售价微涨

文本: 由于中秋节临近，蔬菜需求量有所加大，部分蔬菜价格出现了一些波动，蔬菜平均价格小幅上涨
翻译版: As the mid-Autumn festival approaches, vegetable demand has increased, some vegetables price fluctuations, the average price of vegetables rose slightly
判断依据: 由于中秋节临近、价格小幅上涨

文本: 由于春节期间群众购买力集中，蔬菜需求量上升，加之外地蔬菜运输量减少，大部分蔬菜价格有所上涨。
翻译版: Due to the concentration of purchasing power during the Spring Festival, the demand for vegetables increased, and the transportation of vegetables in the field decreased, the price of most vegetables rose.
判断依据: 春节期间群众购买力集中、价格有所上涨

文本: 近期菜价上涨原因主要有：夏季正值蔬菜需求旺季，加之受端午节日效应影响，近期蔬菜需求增加。
翻译版: The recent rise in vegetable prices mainly include: Summer is the season of vegetable demand, coupled with the day of the Dragon Boat Festival effect, the recent increase in vegetable demand.
判断依据: 受端午节日效应影响、菜格上涨

文本: 蔬菜价格上涨主要原因：一是上周我市气温下降，导致本地蔬菜上市量减少；二是端午期间，对蔬菜的需求量增大。
翻译版: Vegetable price rise main reason: First, last week, the temperature of our city decreased, which led to the decrease of local vegetables market, the second is the Dragon Boat Festival, the demand for vegetables increased.
判断依据: 端午期间、价格上涨

文本: 年末喜庆日子多蔬菜需求量大，市场整体格局供不应求，也一定程度上导致价格趋高。
翻译版: At the end of the festive days of large demand for vegetables, the overall pattern of market demand, but also to a certain extent lead to price high.
判断依据: 年末喜庆日子多、价格趋高

文本: 春节期间，广州蔬菜价格连续上涨，部分叶菜类价格一度超过了同等重量的肉类。
翻译版: During the spring Festival, vegetable prices in Guangzhou continued to rise, and some leaf vegetables were once more than the same weight of meat.
判断依据: 春节期间、价格连续上涨

文本: 春节期间，受雨天寒潮和春节蔬菜需求量大的影响，东莞蔬菜价格一路飙升，20元/斤的荷兰豆甚至比13元/斤的猪肉还要贵。
翻译版: During the Spring Festival, the impact of cold wave and spring Festival vegetable demand, Dongguan vegetable prices soaring, 20 yuan/kg of Dutch beans even 13 yuan/catty of pork is more expensive.
判断依据: 春节期间、价格一路飙升

文本: 春节期间，全国瓜豆类蔬菜需求升高，导致本地叶菜价格也出现大幅上涨。
翻译版: During the Spring Festival, the national demand for vegetables and legumes increased, resulting in a sharp rise in local leaf vegetables prices.
判断依据: 春季期间、价格大幅上涨

文本: 春节期间走亲访友，对蔬菜需求量大，导致供小于求，从而价格上涨。
翻译版: During the spring Festival to visit relatives and friends, the demand for vegetables, resulting in supply less than seeking, thereby rising prices.
判断依据: 春节期间走亲访友、价格上涨

文本: 春节期间，市民的购买需求出现了一定程度的井喷，再加上季节因素影响，运输费用增加，综合推动了蔬菜价格的上扬。
翻译版: During the Spring Festival, the public's purchase demand has appeared a certain degree of blowout, coupled with seasonal factors, transport costs increased, the comprehensive promotion of vegetable prices.
判断依据: 春节期间、价格上扬

文本: 春节期间蔬菜价格普遍上涨的主要原因：二是节日需求旺盛，蔬菜消费量增加；
翻译版: The main reason for the general increase of vegetable prices during the Spring Festival: second, the festival demand is vigorous, vegetable consumption increases;
判断依据: 春节期间、价格普遍上涨

文本: 春节期间我省蔬菜价格普遍上涨，二是节日需求旺盛，蔬菜消费量增加。
翻译版: During the spring Festival, vegetable prices in our province generally rose, the second is strong holiday demand, vegetable consumption increased.
判断依据: 春节期间、价格普遍上涨

文本: 随着元旦、春节的临近，市民蔬菜消费量的增加，后期蔬菜价格还会有上涨趋势。
翻译版: Along with New Year's Day, the spring Festival approaching, the citizen vegetable consumption increases, the later period vegetable price also may have the upward tendency.
判断依据: 元旦、春节的临近、价格上扬

文本: 对于蔬菜市场价格的上涨，主要是临近年末，市场消费量陡增
翻译版: For vegetable market price rise, main is near year end, market consumption is steep
判断依据: 临近年末、价格上涨

文本: 造成本轮价格上涨的原因：二是节日临近消费量增加。春节临近，居民蔬菜消费量大幅上升，市场需求旺盛，拉动价格上涨。
翻译版: The reason why this round of price rise: Second, the festival near consumption increases. The Spring Festival is approaching, the resident vegetable consumption rises sharply, the market demand is exuberant, pulls the price to rise.
判断依据: 节日临近、价格上涨

文本: 春节临近，居民蔬菜消费量大幅上升，市场需求旺盛，拉动价格上涨。而天气因素不利于运输。
翻译版: The Spring Festival is approaching, the resident vegetable consumption rises sharply, the market demand is exuberant, pulls the price to rise. And weather factors are not conducive to transport.
判断依据: 春节临近、价格上涨

文本: 在“双节”传统消费习俗下，蔬菜消费量价齐升，其中外地蔬菜价格涨幅较大。
翻译版: Under the traditional consumption custom of "double section", Vegetable consumption price is rising, and vegetable price in the field is higher.
判断依据: 在“双节”传统消费习俗下、消费量价齐升

文本: 随着春节的临近,市民对蔬菜的消费量增大,蔬菜价格开始明显上涨。
翻译版: With the spring festival approaching, the consumption of vegetables increased, and vegetable prices began to rise markedly.
判断依据: 随着春节的临近、价格明显上涨

文本: 春节临近，居民蔬菜消费量大幅上升，市场需求旺盛，拉动价格上涨。
翻译版: The Spring Festival is approaching, the resident vegetable consumption rises sharply, the market demand is exuberant, pulls the price to rise.
判断依据: 春节临近、价格上涨

文本: 春节临近，居民蔬菜消费量大幅上升，市场需求旺盛，拉动价格上涨。
翻译版: The Spring Festival is approaching, the resident vegetable consumption rises sharply, the market demand is exuberant, pulls the price to rise.
判断依据: 消费量大幅上升、价格上涨

文本: 春节过后，广州32种主要蔬菜综合零售均价一直缓慢上升
翻译版: After the Spring Festival, the average retail price of 32 main vegetables in Guangzhou has been slowly rising
判断依据: 春节过后、综合零售均价一直缓慢上升

文本: 元旦临近，蔬菜需求增加，蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: New Year's Day approaches, vegetable demand increases, vegetable prices rise.
判断依据: 元旦临近、蔬菜价格上涨

文本: 受天气和节日效应等影响，菜价整体上出现了上涨
翻译版: Influenced by weather and holiday effects, the price of vegetables rose on the whole.
判断依据: 节日效应、菜价整体上出现了上涨

文本: 而节后蔬菜需求增加。从10月7日开始，随着人员返程，需求增加明显。供不应求的局面初见，从而推动价格上升。
翻译版: The demand for vegetables is increasing. From October 7 onwards, with the return of personnel, demand increased significantly. Demand has been in short supply, pushing up prices.
判断依据: 节后蔬菜需求增加、价格上涨

文本: 国庆假期，喜宴、婚宴较集中，各大酒店蔬菜需求量增加，虽然蔬菜上市量逐步增多，但蔬菜价格相比国庆节前仍旧呈稳中上涨趋势。
翻译版: National Day holiday, banquet, wedding banquet more concentrated, the hotel demand for vegetables increased, although the number of vegetables listed gradually increased, but the price of vegetables in comparison with the national day is still stable in the upward trend.
判断依据: 国庆期间、价格稳中上涨

文本: “中秋节”前后终端消费需求有所增加，同时外省市蔬菜调入增加了运输成本，因此促使了蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Mid-Autumn Festival before and after the end of consumption demand increased, while the provinces and vegetables to increase the transportation costs, so the price of vegetables to increase.
判断依据: 中秋节前后消费需求有所增加、价格上涨

文本: 随着元宵节的过去，昨天大部分蔬菜的批发价开始普遍下降，绝大部分蔬菜下降了近2成左右

判断依据: 随着元宵节的过去、批发价开始普遍下降

文本: 受中秋节的影响，市场需求增加，近两天菜价可能会有小幅上涨。
翻译版: Influenced by the Mid-Autumn Festival, the market demand increases, the price of vegetables in the last two days may be slightly higher.

文本: 随着中秋节临近，城区消费市场需求强劲，不少商品陆续迎来“节日涨”。
翻译版: With the Mid-Autumn festival approaching, the urban consumer market demand is strong, many commodities have ushered in "festival Rise".

文本: 中秋将至,蔬菜消费市场下游需求强劲,加之蔬菜处于夏秋品种交接之际,菜价看涨。
翻译版: Mid-Autumn Festival will be, vegetable consumption market downstream demand is strong, coupled with vegetables in the summer and autumn varieties handover, vegetable prices are bullish.

文本: 春节临近需求旺盛，我市菜篮子价格呈现涨势。
翻译版: The spring Festival near demand is exuberant, our city basket price presents the rally.
判断依据: 春节临近、价格呈现涨势

文本: 受气温降低和元宵节因素影响，江城蔬菜价格节后并未走低，仍在高位运行，多个品种蔬菜价格甚至上涨。
翻译版: Under the influence of temperature and lantern Festival, the price of vegetables in Jiangcheng was not lower, still running at high level, and the price of many varieties of vegetables rose even.

文本: 受春节节日效应的影响，节日期间我市蔬菜的需求量增大，造成蔬菜价格居高不下
翻译版: Influenced by the Spring Festival effect, the demand for vegetables in our city increased, resulting in high vegetable prices
判断依据: 春节节日效应的影响、价格居高不下

文本: 春节期间蔬菜供应充足，因节日消费需求旺盛，价格环比将继续呈上扬态势。
翻译版: During the Spring Festival, the supply of vegetables is plentiful, because of the strong holiday consumption demand, the price chain will continue to rise.

文本: 随着春节临近，市场需求转旺，部分蔬菜价格持续上涨。
翻译版: As the Spring Festival approaches, market demand is booming and some vegetable prices continue to rise.
判断依据: 春节临近、价格持续上涨

文本: 受外调量增加运输成本上升、节前市场需求旺盛等因素影响，蔬菜价格整体小幅上涨。
翻译版: By the increase in the volume of transport costs, before the market demand for strong factors such as the overall small increase in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 节前市场需求旺盛、价格小幅上涨

文本: 气温下降蔬菜供应量减少，春节临近需求增加等因素相互叠加，导致蔬菜价格出现上涨
翻译版: By the increase in the volume of transport costs, before the market demand for strong factors such as the overall small increase in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 春节临近需求增加、价格出现上涨

文本: 岁末年初，蔬菜需求相对增强，居民采购量加大，菜价正常性攀升
翻译版: At the end of the year, the demand for vegetables increased, the amount of residents purchase increased, the normal price of vegetables Rose

文本: 春节临近、需求增加等系列因素，导致蔬菜价格出现上涨。
翻译版: The Spring Festival draws near, the demand increases and so on series of factors, causes the vegetable price to appear to rise.

文本: 由于中秋节临近，蔬菜需求量有所加大，部分蔬菜价格出现了一些波动，蔬菜平均价格小幅上涨
翻译版: As the mid-Autumn festival approaches, vegetable demand has increased, some vegetables price fluctuations, the average price of vegetables rose slightly

文本: 恰逢元旦假日天气好转，需求量有所增多，蔬菜价格因而上扬。
翻译版: On New Year's Day holiday weather improved, demand increased, vegetable prices rose.

文本: 国庆长假带动蔬菜需求增长，菜价总体稳中微升。
翻译版: National Day holiday led to the growth of vegetable demand, vegetable prices overall stability in micro-rise.
判断依据: 国庆长假、菜价总体稳中微升

文本: 受中秋、国庆的节日效应影响，预计消费者蔬菜需求量将会增加，蔬菜价格面临上涨压力。
翻译版: By the Mid-Autumn festival, National Day holiday effect, expected to increase consumer demand for vegetables, vegetable prices face rising pressure.
判断依据: 节日效应影响、价格面临上涨压力

文本: 受传统节日“春节”的影响，市场消费需求旺盛，拉动了蔬菜价格的上涨。
翻译版: Influenced by the traditional festival "Spring Festival", the market demand is booming, which drives the price of vegetable to rise.
判断依据: 春节的影响、拉动了价格的上涨

文本: 春节期间，由于市民对蔬菜需求量较大，加之天气寒冷使得蔬菜运藏成本增加，造成蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: During the Spring Festival, because of the public demand for vegetables, coupled with the cold weather to increase the cost of vegetable storage, resulting in higher vegetable prices.
判断依据: 春节期间、价格上涨

文本: 随着入冬后寒潮的持续到来以及元旦和春节的临近，蔬菜需求量越来越大，预计整体菜价仍会小幅走高。
翻译版: As the cold wave continues to follow the winter and New Year's Day and the spring Festival approaching, vegetables demand is growing, the overall price is expected to still slightly higher.
判断依据: 元旦和春节的临近、菜价小幅走高

文本: 岁末年初，春节节日市场效应逐步显现，市场需求将日趋旺盛，预计春节后蔬菜交易价格将继续呈上涨态势。
翻译版: At the end of the year, the Spring Festival festival market effect gradually appeared, the market demand will become more and more exuberant, the vegetable trade price is expected to continue to rise after the Spring festival.
判断依据: 节日市场效应逐步显现、价格呈上涨态势

文本: 春节过后市场需求减弱，蛋品与蔬菜价格总体继续呈现小幅回落的态势。
翻译版: After the Spring Festival market demand weakened, egg and vegetable prices overall continued to show a small decline in the situation.
判断依据: 春节过后、价格总体小幅回落

文本: 随着新春来临，海口的蔬菜价格一路上扬
翻译版: With the advent of the spring, the price of vegetables in Haikou rose
判断依据: 新春来临、价格一路上扬

文本: 中秋节、国庆节临近，“菜篮子”需求量将明显增加，价格将呈规律性小幅上涨。
翻译版: Mid-Autumn Festival, National Day near, "basket" demand will increase significantly, the price will be a small increase in regularity.
判断依据: 中秋节、国庆节临近、价格呈规律性小幅上涨

文本: 临近春节，又受降雪天气影响，延安蔬菜价格明显上涨。
翻译版: Near the Spring Festival, also affected by snowfall, the price of Yan ' an vegetables rose significantly.
判断依据: 临近春节、价格明显上涨

文本: 后期临近春节，需求将持续增加，如无恶劣天气影响，在蔬菜上市量正常情况下，预计价格将呈稳中有升走势运行
翻译版: In the late spring Festival, the demand will continue to increase, such as no adverse weather effects, in the normal case of vegetables listed, the expected price will be stable in the rising trend of operation
判断依据: 临近春节、价格稳中有升

文本: 元旦期间蔬菜需求相对增加，促进菜价上涨。
翻译版: New Year's Day vegetable demand increases relatively, promote vegetable price to rise.
判断依据: 元旦期间、菜价上涨

文本: 春节前后，市民消费需求增大，加之天气、需求等因素影响，市区蔬菜价格有可能还将一路看涨
翻译版: Before and after the Spring festival, consumer demand increased, coupled with the weather, demand and other factors, the price of vegetables in the city may still be bullish
判断依据: 春节前后、价格一路看涨

文本: 后期，随着元旦的到来，渭南市蔬菜需求量增加，加之数九寒天，气温越来越低，外地蔬菜调运成本上升，蔬菜价格还会有小幅上升趋势。
翻译版: Later, with the advent of New Year's Day, Weinan vegetables demand increase, coupled with dread, the temperature is getting lower, the field vegetable transportation costs rise, vegetable prices will have a small upward trend.
判断依据: 元旦、价格有小幅上升趋势

文本: 中秋节”前后终端消费需求有所增加，同时外省市蔬菜调入增加了运输成本，因此促使了蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Mid-Autumn Festival "the demand for terminal consumption has increased, while the import of vegetables in other provinces increased transport costs, which led to a rise in vegetable prices."
判断依据: 中秋节、价格上涨

文本: 另一方面，由于中秋和国庆的影响，市场需求量有所增加。10月份国庆期间，因为节日影响，菜价将会保持高位运行。
翻译版: On the other hand, due to the impact of the Mid-Autumn Festival and the National Day, market demand has increased. During the national day of October, the price of vegetables will stay high for the holiday season.
判断依据: 中秋和国庆的影响、菜价保持高位运行

文本: 随着“双节”来临，市场需求量又增加不少，蔬菜价格才一直维持在较高水平。
翻译版: With the advent of "double festival", market demand has increased a lot, vegetable prices have been maintained at a higher level.
判断依据: 双节来临、价格维持在较高水平

文本: 此外，由于今年中秋节较往年提前，节庆效应也拉动了菜价上涨。
翻译版: In addition, as the Mid-Autumn Festival earlier this year than in previous years, festive effect also led to the rise in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 中秋节、菜价上涨

文本: 城乡人口结构变动及城乡人均果蔬产品消费的差异推动了果蔬总需求的上涨，进而拉升了果蔬产品的市场价格。
翻译版: The change of urban and rural population structure and the difference of consumption of fruit and vegetable products in urban and rural areas promoted the total demand of fruits and vegetables, and then the market price of fruit and vegetable products.
判断依据: 人口结构变动、拉升了果蔬产品的市场价格

文本: 节后院校开学企业开工，外来人口增多，对蔬菜需求量有所增加。
翻译版: After the start of the opening of the university, the external population increased, the demand for vegetables increased.
判断依据: 外来人口增多、价格上涨

文本: 兰州市的流动人口也是逐年递增，这样蔬菜需求量越来越大，供需矛盾越来越突出。随着需求量的增加，菜价也开始“水涨船高”。
翻译版: The floating population of Lanzhou city is increasing yearly, so the demand for vegetables is more and more serious. As demand increased, the price of vegetables began to rise.
判断依据: 流动人口逐年递增、菜价“水涨船高”

文本: 近年来随着城镇化建设速度的加快，城镇人口逐年增加，城镇蔬菜需求量快速增加。
翻译版: In recent years, with the rapid development of urbanization, the urban population has increased, and the demand for vegetable has increased rapidly.
判断依据: 人口逐年增加、价格上涨

文本: 随着城市化进程加快，城市规模扩大，大量外来人口进入城市，在人口增加的同时，蔬菜的需求量也在大幅增长，使城市的消费压力相应加大，也带动了蔬菜价格的上涨。
翻译版: With the acceleration of urbanization, the expansion of urban scale, a large number of foreign population into the city, the increase in the population at the same time, the demand for vegetables has also increased sharply, so that the city's consumption pressure correspondingly increased, but also led to the rise in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 大量外来人口进入城市、带动了蔬菜价格的增长

文本: 随着我国城镇人口数量不断增长，尤其是大量农民工进城务工，带动蔬菜消费量也相应较快增长。
翻译版: With the increasing number of urban population in China, especially the large number of migrant workers working in cities, the consumption of vegetables is also increasing rapidly.
判断依据: 城镇人口数量不断增长、价格上涨

文本: 近年来，随着城市规模的快速扩展，市区常驻人口和外来人口不断增加，人民生活水平提高，以菜为主的清谈饮食理念有所增强，蔬菜市场需求量不断增大，也是价格上扬的推手。
翻译版: In recent years, with the rapid expansion of the urban scale, the resident population and the external population of the urban area are increasing, the people's living standard is improved, the vegetable market demand is increasing and the price is rising.
判断依据: 人口不断增加、价格上扬

文本: 随着人感染H7N9禽流感疫情的持续，江苏省蔬菜消费量明显增加，蔬菜价格继续上涨,但涨势有所放缓
翻译版: With the H7N9 of the avian influenza epidemic, the vegetable consumption in Jiangsu Province increased significantly, and vegetable prices continued to rise, but the rally slowed.
判断依据: H7N9禽流感疫情的持续、价格继续上涨

文本: 近期活禽市场陆续关闭或自动休市，肉、禽、蛋消费明显减少，价格下跌；水产品和蔬菜需求旺盛，价格上涨
翻译版: In the near future, the live poultry market has been closed down or auto-closing, and the consumption of meat, poultry and eggs has decreased significantly, and prices have fallen.
判断依据: 活禽市场陆续关闭或自动休市、价格上涨

文本: 清明节后，由于“春菜采尽、夏菜刚种”，同时受到禽流感影响，禽类销售量骤减、蔬菜需求量猛增，湖南部分市州的蔬菜供应出现“青黄不接”、菜价骤涨态势。
翻译版: After the Ching Ming Festival, due to "spring vegetables harvest, summer vegetables just species", at the same time affected by avian flu, poultry sales plummeted, the demand for vegetables soared, Hunan province, some of the city's vegetables supply appeared "lean", vegetable prices rose.
判断依据: 受到禽流感的影响、价格骤涨

文本: 本周蔬菜的整体价格稳中有升，一是仍受禽流感的影响，市民对禽肉类的需求减少，对蔬菜的需求加大，造成蔬菜的价格上涨
翻译版: This week, the overall price of vegetables rose steadily, one is still affected by avian flu, the public demand for poultry meat is reduced, the demand for vegetables increased, resulting in higher prices of vegetables
判断依据: 受禽流感的影响、价格上涨

文本: 受H7N9禽流感影响，居民蔬菜消费量增加，上周我省大部分蔬菜价格略有上涨。
翻译版: Affected by H7N9 avian flu, consumption of vegetables increased, last week, most of our vegetables prices rose slightly.
判断依据: 受H7N9禽流感影响、价格略有上涨

文本: 随着人感染H7N9禽流感疫情的持续，禽类、蛋类产品交易量近期持续减少，蛋鸡和肉鸡养殖业效益大幅下滑，蔬菜价格继续上涨,但涨势有所放缓。上周，全省蔬菜消费量明显增加。
翻译版: As human infection H7N9 avian influenza epidemic, poultry, egg products trading continued to decline in recent days, layers and broiler aquaculture benefits fell sharply, vegetable prices continue to rise, but the rally has slowed. Last week, the province's vegetable consumption increased markedly.
判断依据: H7N9禽流感疫情的持续、价格继续上涨

文本: 普通大蒜借甲流“上位”成蔬菜“贵族” 由于今年世界范围内的流感大爆发，国外民众也爱上了大蒜，市场对大蒜的需求量暴增。
翻译版: Ordinary garlic by the "upper" into a vegetable "nobility" due to the outbreak of influenza worldwide this year, foreign people also fell in love with garlic, the market demand for garlic increased.
判断依据: 流感大爆发、上位成蔬菜贵族

文本: 受3月底爆发的H7N9禽流感疫情影响，杭州禽类市场需求大幅下降，蔬菜、水产等替代副食品短期内需求明显增长，价格上涨
翻译版: Affected by the outbreak of H7N9 avian influenza in late March, the demand for Hangzhou poultry market has fallen sharply, and the demand for vegetables, aquatic products and other substitutes for non-staple food has obviously increased in the short term.
判断依据: H7N9禽流感疫情影响、价格上涨

文本: 今夏“姜你军”成为市场“炙手可热”的农产品，价格持续上涨，创出１０年最高。姜价奇高的背后，是去年“毒生姜”事件的后遗症。
翻译版: This summer, "Ginger You Army" become the market "hot" agricultural products, prices continue to rise, the highest 10 years. The high price of ginger behind, is the last year "poison Ginger" incident Sequela.
判断依据: 毒生姜事件后遗症、价格持续上涨

文本: “毒生姜”风波平息 武汉生姜价格翻倍上涨
翻译版: Poison Ginger storm to quell the price of Wuhan Ginger doubled.
判断依据: 毒生姜风波平息、价格翻倍上涨

文本: 受山东潍坊峡山区“毒生姜”事件影响，兰州生姜批发、零售市场出现不同程度滞销，大青山蔬菜瓜果批发市场的生姜价格从上周的每斤2元以上降到近日的1.8元左右，批发量也较往常减少了一半
翻译版: By the Shandong Weifang Gorge Mountain "poisonous Ginger" The incident influence, Lanzhou Ginger Wholesale, the retail market appears the different degree unsalable, the big castle Peak vegetable Fruit Wholesale market The ginger price from last week's each catty more than 2 yuan to the recent 1.8 yuan, the wholesale quantity also reduced half by the usual
判断依据: 受毒生姜事件影响、价格下降

文本: 以生姜为例：生姜未到上市期，同时受到去年山东毒生姜事件影响导致价格过快上涨。
翻译版: Take Ginger as an example: Ginger was not listed, and was affected by last year's poisoning of ginger in Shandong Province.
判断依据: 受到去年山东毒生姜事件影响导致价格过快上涨。
来源: 中华人民共和国商务部

文本: 受疫情影响，禽类市场需求下降，蔬菜需求量增加，带动菜价小幅上涨。
翻译版: Affected by the epidemic, poultry market demand has decreased, vegetable demand increased, led to a small increase in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 受疫情影响、菜价小幅上涨

文本: 受到禽流感的影响，不少市民对蔬菜的需求量变大，因此蔬菜价格很难下降，而且还出现了小幅度上升。
翻译版: Affected by the avian flu, many people's demand for vegetables has become larger, so vegetable prices are very difficult to fall and there has been a small increase.
判断依据: 禽流感的影响、价格小幅度上升

文本: 近期外地发生禽流感，市民们对蔬菜的需求量大增致使供求矛盾导致23种蔬菜价格与4月3日相比全部上涨。
翻译版: The recent outbreak of avian flu in the field and the increasing demand for vegetables have led to a contradiction between supply and demand, resulting in 23 vegetable prices rising all over April 3.
判断依据: 发生禽流感、全部上涨

文本: 随着人感染H7N9禽流感疫情的持续，江苏省蔬菜消费量明显增加，蔬菜价格继续上涨,但涨势有所放缓
翻译版: With the H7N10 of the avian influenza epidemic, the vegetable consumption in Jiangsu Province increased significantly, and vegetable prices continued to rise, but the rally slowed.
判断依据: 消费量明显增加、价格继续上涨

文本: 在春节期间，蔬菜需求旺盛，价格呈上涨趋势
翻译版: During the Spring Festival, the demand for vegetables is strong and the price is rising.
判断依据: 需求旺盛、价格呈上涨趋势

文本: 本周汕头天气炎热无雨，本地菜上市量减少，加上肉类价格上涨使得蔬菜需求量增加，蔬菜价格继续上升。
翻译版: This week, the weather is hot and rainy in Shantou, the local dish is on the decline, and the price of meat increases, and vegetable prices continue to rise.
判断依据: 需求量增加、价格继续上升

文本: 前段时期株洲市菜源主供地如广西、云南或水灾或旱灾，蔬菜输出地一时成了蔬菜需求地，导致菜价上扬。
翻译版: In the previous period, the main source of Zhuzhou vegetables, such as Guangxi, Yunnan, or floods or droughts, vegetable exports to the demand for vegetables, resulting in a rise in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 输出地转需求地、价格上扬

文本: 一连数天的阴雨天气以及学校开学对蔬菜需求量的陡然增大，使得我市一些蔬菜的价格持续看涨
翻译版: A few days of rainy weather and a sudden increase in school demand for vegetables, making some vegetables in our city prices continue to bullish
判断依据: 需求量的陡然增大、价格持续看涨

文本: 雨天造成的蔬菜采摘、运输不便，市场供求量相对减少，加之各类学校集中开学，蔬菜需求量明显增加等多重因素导致菜价一路上扬。
翻译版: Rainy day caused by the vegetable picking, transportation inconvenience, market supply and demand is relatively reduced, together with all types of schools, vegetable demand increased significantly, such as multiple factors led to the rise in prices.
判断依据: 需求明显增加导致菜价一路上扬

文本: “中秋节、国庆节”的到来，拉动市场蔬菜需求量不断加大，蔬菜价格小幅上涨。
翻译版: "Mid-Autumn Festival, National Day" arrival, pulling the market demand for vegetables is increasing, vegetable prices rose slightly.
判断依据: 需求量不断增大、价格小幅上涨

文本: 上周周末的突然降温降雨，蔬菜需求量大增，但不少品种因产地降雨影响货品进场，货源减少后导致蔬菜价格整体上扬
翻译版: Last weekend's sudden cooling rain, vegetable demand increased, but many varieties due to the origin of the impact of the rain goods into the market, the decrease in the price of vegetables led to the overall rise
判断依据: 需求量大增、价格整体上扬

文本: 临近月末，新年将至，蔬菜需求量开始加大，也是价格上涨的原因之一。
翻译版: Near the end of the month, the new year, vegetable demand began to increase, is also one of the reasons for the price rise.
判断依据: 需求量开始加大、价格上涨

文本: 从年前两周开始，各类蔬菜的价格就出现了明显上涨，此次上涨幅度较大的原因是因为受到新年蔬菜需求量猛增和天气的影响。
翻译版: Since the beginning of the year two weeks, the price of various vegetables has risen significantly, the increase is due to a large rise in the new Year vegetable demand and the impact of the weather.
判断依据: 需求量猛增、价格就出现了明显上涨

文本: 节后的一段时期内，居民家中肉、蛋类食品仍有储藏，日常必需品采购以新鲜蔬菜为主，蔬菜需求量居高不下
翻译版: After a period of time, the residents of the meat, eggs, food is still stored, daily necessities to buy fresh vegetables, the high demand for vegetables
判断依据: 需求高居不下、价格回升

文本: 随着近日强冷空气的到来，市场对大棚菜和外地蔬菜需求量加大，蔬菜价格小幅上涨
翻译版: With the advent of strong cold air, the market for greenhouse vegetables and vegetable demand increased, vegetable prices rose slightly
判断依据: 需求量加大、价格小幅上涨

文本: 上周恰逢元旦小长假，蔬菜需求明显扩大，我省重点监测的18种蔬菜中有15种蔬菜价格上涨
翻译版: Last week coincides with a New Year's Day holiday, vegetable demand has widened significantly, our province 18 kinds of vegetables to monitor the price of 16 kinds of vegetables Rose
判断依据: 需求明显扩大、价格上涨

文本: 临近圣诞节，作为“圣诞果”的苹果市场需求量增大，而苹果的库存量有限，所以价格上涨。
翻译版: Near Christmas, Apple's market demand for "Christmas fruit" increased, while Apple's stock was limited, so prices rose.
判断依据: 苹果市场需求量增大、价格上涨

文本: 气温的不断变动直接影响了蔬菜价格的波动，加上“春节”的临近，市场交易量明显上升，蔬菜整体价格也因此有所上涨

翻译版: The reason for the increase in vegetable prices is: With the gradual recovery of the temperature, the consumption of meat and eggs is declining, the proportion of vegetable consumption increases and the market demand is increasing.
判断依据: 蔬菜消费比重增大、价格上涨

文本: 中秋节、国庆节临近，“菜篮子”需求量将明显增加，价格将呈规律性小幅上涨。

判断依据: 市场需求大、价格微涨

文本: 由于近期季节性蔬菜属于青黄不接阶段，导致蔬菜生产量少，市场消费需求量量并未减少，出现供不应求，造成蔬菜价格上涨。
翻译版: Because the recent seasonal vegetables belong to the lean stage, resulting in less vegetable production, the market demand for consumption has not decreased, the emergence of short supply, resulting in higher vegetable prices.
判断依据: 消费需求量并未减少、价格上涨

文本: 目前，春节长假结束，企业开始陆续开工投产，学校将迎开学季，预计新一轮采购高峰开始后，蔬菜需求将会增加，短期蔬菜价格仍将维持高位运行。
翻译版: At present, the end of the Chinese New Year holiday, the enterprise began to start production, the school will welcome the start of the season, is expected to the next round of procurement peak, vegetable demand will increase, short-term vegetable prices will remain high operation.
判断依据: 采购高峰、价格维持高位运行

文本: 但未来几天随着外来务工人员集中返回，市场需求量的不断增加，蔬菜价格应该还会有所回升
翻译版: But in the next few days, with the concentration of migrant workers returning, market demand is increasing, vegetable prices should also be a rebound
判断依据: 需求量不断增加、价格有所回升

文本: 随着全市低温雨雪天气增多和春节的到来，广大市民需求量增加，预计一月份全市蔬菜批发价格还会继续呈上行走势。
翻译版: With the city's low temperature, rain and snow and the arrival of the Spring Festival, the general public demand increased, the city of January is expected to continue the wholesale price of vegetables to the trend.
判断依据: 需求量增加、价格呈上行走势

文本: 元旦期间蔬菜需求相对增加，促进菜价上涨。

翻译版: Before and after the Spring festival, consumer demand increased, coupled with the weather, demand and other factors, the price of vegetables in the city may still be bullish

文本: 6月随着山东主产区新蒜上市，受减产消息的刺激，大蒜经销商抢购大蒜，导致大蒜价格一路上涨。

对应指标: 消费者的生活习惯和偏好
判断依据: 为预防“秋燥”、价格继续上涨

文本: 菜价上涨主要是季节性因素所致。随着天气转冷，省内本地大田蔬菜上市已接近尾声，对外地蔬菜需求量相对加大。

文本: 食用菌等价格的上涨很大程度是由新年火锅季催生的需求上涨引起的。

文本: 城乡居民生活水平高和健康环保观念增强，对蔬菜品种和质量要求越来越高，尤其是对绿色无公害、高品质的有机食品和反季节蔬菜需求越来越多。
