翻译版: Vegetable market trade is unusually hot (the entry volume continues to grow for four consecutive weeks), the overall price fluctuation is not big. Demand factor: With the opening of tertiary institutions and the proximity of traditional festivals, the demand has increased greatly, which drives the growth of the vegetable market volume.
判断依据: 交易异常火爆、整体菜价波动不大

文本: 蔬菜市场交易异常火爆（进场量连续四周持续增长），整体菜价波动不大。需求因素：随着大专院校的开学及传统节日的临近，需求量大幅增加，带动蔬菜市场交易量的增长。
翻译版: Vegetable market trade is unusually hot (the entry volume continues to grow for four consecutive weeks), the overall price fluctuation is not big. Demand factor: With the opening of tertiary institutions and the proximity of traditional festivals, the demand has increased greatly, which drives the growth of the vegetable market volume.
判断依据: 传统节日的临近、整体菜价波动不大

文本: 由于应季蔬菜不断上市，国庆节即将来临，预测蔬菜价格变化会保持平稳的幅度。
翻译版: Due to seasonal vegetables on the market, National Day is coming, the prediction of vegetable price changes will maintain a stable range.
判断依据: 国庆节即将来临、预测价格变化会保持平稳的幅度

文本: 春节前蔬菜市场供应充足 价格保持平稳态势
翻译版: The vegetable market before the Spring Festival adequate supply of prices to maintain a steady trend
判断依据: 春节、价格保持平稳态势

文本: 上周，蔬菜市场储备充足，交易红火，整体菜价稳定。
翻译版: Last week, the vegetable market was well stocked and trading was booming. The overall vegetable price was stable.
判断依据: 交易红火、整体菜价稳定

文本: 一、切实强化“菜篮子”市长负责制。二、加强蔬菜生产基地建设。三、改善蔬菜流通设施条件。四、落实和完善“绿色通道”政策。五、提高蔬菜产销组织化程度。六、强化蔬菜信息体系建设。8月17日，在商务部召开的新闻发布会上，新闻发言人姚坚指出，商务部监测的18种蔬菜平均批发价格同比上涨49.7%，涨幅分别比6月份扩大13.7个百分点。
翻译版: First, strengthen the "vegetable basket" mayor responsibility system. Second, strengthen the vegetable production base construction. Third, improve the conditions of vegetable circulation facilities. Fourth, implement and improve the "green channel" policy. Fifth, improve the level of vegetable production and marketing. Sixth, strengthen the vegetable information system. August 17, at the Ministry of Commerce held a press conference, spokesman Yao Jian pointed out that the Ministry of Commerce to monitor the 18 kinds of vegetables, the average wholesale price rose 49.7%, respectively, or more than in June to expand 13.7 percentage points.
判断依据: 落实和完善“绿色通道”、蔬菜平均批发价格同比上涨

文本: 二是全国性的通货膨胀压力导致种子、化肥、农药、人工等成本快速上升，直接引起蔬菜价格上涨
翻译版: Second, the national inflationary pressures lead to seeds, fertilizers, pesticides, labor and other costs rise rapidly, a direct result of vegetable prices
判断依据: 通货膨胀压力、价格上涨

文本: 菜价高了，“进口费”涨了，“菜奴”、“果奴”冒出来了。通胀压力已经从专家口中的数字变为普通人的“体感”。
翻译版: Vegetable prices high, "import costs" up, "vegetable slave", "fruit slave" came out. Inflationary pressures have changed from the figures in the mouth to the "somatosensory" of ordinary people.
判断依据: 菜价高了、通胀压力

文本: 据广州市菜篮子价格信息最新统计数据显示，约62.3％的蔬菜出现不同程度涨价，部分涨幅在100％以上。与此同时，“内地恶性通胀或已爆发”的言论不胫而走。
翻译版: According to the Guangzhou City vegetable basket price information the latest statistics show that about 62.3% of the vegetables appear in varying degrees of price increases, some rose more than 100%. At the same time, "the mainland of malignant inflation or outbreak," the remarks spread like wildfire
判断依据: 蔬菜、不同程度涨价、内地恶性通胀

文本: 同时，过多的流转环节仍是蔬菜价格居高不下的重要原因。以寿光为例，蔬菜从田间运到物流园后，至少还要倒手3次才能出现在全国各地消费市场的终端。
翻译版: At the same time, too much circulation is still an important reason for high vegetable prices. To Shouguang, for example, vegetables transported from the field to the logistics park, at least three times to be able to appear in the consumer market across the country terminal.
判断依据: 过多的流转环节、蔬菜价格居高不下

文本: 根据我十多年的批发经验，菜价过高是因为其中的运行环节太多，层层加价。”他掰着手指头说，蔬菜从地里、大棚里出来，要雇人采摘、雇车运输，随后有高速公路费、市场进场费等，菜到了消费者手里自然抬高了价格。
翻译版: According to my more than 10 years of wholesale experience, vegetable prices are too high because of the operation of which too many layers of fare increases. "He broke his fingers, said vegetables from the ground, shed out, to hire people to pick, hire car transport, followed by highway fees, market entry fees, etc., to the consumer in the hands of consumers naturally raise the price.
判断依据: 菜价过高、运行环节太多

文本: 货币供应量对白菜、黄瓜、西红柿、菜椒和四季豆价格长期上涨趋势的贡献分别为38% ,42% ,40% ,40%和38%;对苹果、香蕉和橙子价格长期上涨趋势的贡献分别为37 % , 49%和44 %，最低的贡献比例也超过了1 /3
翻译版: The contribution of the money supply to the long-term upward trend in cabbage, cucumber, tomato, vegetable pepper and seasonal beans is 38%, 42%, 40%, 40% and 38% respectively. Contribution to the long-term upward trend in prices for apples, bananas and oranges Respectively, 37%, 49% and 44%, the lowest contribution rate of more than 1/3
判断依据: 货币供应量、上涨

文本: 针对近年来果蔬产品价格的上涨趋势，华中农业大学教授李崇光撰文指出，货币供应量增发、城乡人口结构变动引致的需求变化及生产流通成本上涨等因素扮演非常重要的作用。
翻译版: In view of the rising trend of prices of fruits and vegetables in recent years, Huizhong Agricultural University professor Li Chongguang pointed out that the money supply, urban and rural population structure changes caused by changes in demand and production and circulation costs and other factors play a very important role.
判断依据: 货币供应量、上涨

文本: 近一段时间，不仅猪肉价格连续上涨，禽蛋、粮食、蔬菜、水果等价格，都出现了强劲反弹的势头。专家指出，这在短期将带动CPI上升，并符合国家宏观调控目标，但长期来看，可能是通货膨胀的隐忧。因为货币供应量大增首先会反映在食品价格上涨上面
翻译版: Recently, not only pork prices rose continuously, eggs, food, vegetables, fruits and other prices, there has been a strong rebound in the momentum. Experts pointed out that this will lead to CPI rise in the short term, and in line with national macro-control targets, but the long term, may be the worries of inflation. Because the money supply will be reflected in the first increase in food prices above
判断依据: 价格连续上涨、货币供应量

文本: 2012年年底，郑州首批10家平价蔬菜超市正式开张营业，菜价低、菜品新鲜，深获市民喜爱。今后，更多郑州市民可以吃到便宜的新鲜蔬菜，记者昨日了解到，郑州市政府印发《郑州市平价蔬菜直通车进社区工作实施方案》，决定在郑州市人口集中且周边商业网点少的小区，开通平价蔬菜直通车，采用“统一采购、统一配送、统一价格、统一标识、统一服务”的方式，直接进入社区，方便群众买菜。
翻译版: The end of 2012, Zhengzhou, the first batch of 10 cheap vegetable supermarket officially opened business, low vegetable prices, fresh dishes, deep by the public favorite. In the future, more people in Zhengzhou can eat cheap fresh vegetables, the reporter learned yesterday, the Zhengzhou municipal government issued the "Zhengzhou City, cheap vegetables into the community through the implementation of the program", decided to focus on the city of Zhengzhou and the surrounding commercial network area , The opening of cheap vegetables through train, the use of "unified procurement, unified distribution, unified price, unified logo, unified service" approach, directly into the community, to facilitate the masses to buy food.
判断依据: 菜价低、菜品新鲜、平价蔬菜超市、郑州市平价蔬菜直通车进社区工作实施方案

文本: 谈及带叶蔬菜降价的原因，业内人士认为，这与各级政府的稳定物价政策和天气因素有关。
翻译版: Talk about the reasons for the price of leafy vegetables, the industry believes that this level of government and the stability of the price policy and weather factors.
判断依据: 蔬菜降价、稳定物价政策

文本: 近期中央、地方接连出招稳定物价 ，打出政策“组合拳”，抑制通胀的措施出台之密集，力度之大，实属罕见。在此推动下，广东主要农产品价格稳中有降，物价涨速放缓。
翻译版: The recent central and local moves to stabilize prices, play the policy "combination boxing", the suppression of inflation measures introduced intensive, the intensity of the large, it is rare. Driven by this, the main agricultural prices in Guangdong steadily, prices slowed down.
判断依据: 抑制通胀、价格稳中有降

文本: 在过去的一个半月时间里，由于菜价涨得比较厉害，厦门市启动了政府差价补贴销售平价蔬菜，在全市57家平价商店以低于市场平均价15%销售蔬菜。
翻译版: In the past one and a half months, due to vegetable prices rose more powerful, Xiamen City, the government spread subsidies to sell cheap vegetables, 57 stores in the city to lower than the average price of 15% of the market sales of vegetables.
判断依据: 政府差价补贴销售、低于市场平均价

文本: 海口近期菜价高涨，市民直言“吃不起”，该市政府5日发布公告，从即日起到春节假期对8种蔬菜实行不限量平价销售。
翻译版: Haikou recent high prices of vegetables, the public speak "can not afford", the city government issued a notice on the 5th, from now on to the Spring Festival holiday on the implementation of eight kinds of vegetables are not limited parity sales.
判断依据: 近期菜价高涨、吃不起、实行不限量平价销售

文本: 在蔬菜批发商老范看来，最近一段时间，国家各项稳定物价的政策出台，蔬菜价格已经有小幅下降，这主要归功于农产品绿色通道的开通。
翻译版: Vegetable wholesalers in the old Fan view, the most recent period, the state of the introduction of the policy of stabilizing prices, vegetable prices have declined slightly, mainly due to the opening of agricultural green channel.
判断依据: 小幅下降、农产品绿色通道

文本: 福州10日开始对大白菜、上海青、豆芽菜和空心菜等4种主要蔬菜实施“限价令”。至11日，福州主要超市全部将菜价调至政府指导价之下，4种大路菜的降价幅度两日间普遍达到15%—50%。
翻译版: Fuzhou 10 days on the cabbage, Shanghai green, bean sprouts and water spinach and other four kinds of vegetables to implement the "limit order." To 11, Fuzhou, the main supermarket prices will be transferred to the government under the guidance of the price, the four kinds of road prices in the two days between the price of 15% -50%.
判断依据: 蔬菜实施“限价令”，降价

文本: 另一方面得益于政府稳定蔬菜价格的扶持政策，主产区销售价格稳中趋降。
翻译版: On the other hand benefited from the government to stabilize the price of vegetables to support the policy, the main producing areas of sales prices steadily down.
判断依据: 蔬菜价格、扶持政策、价格稳中趋降

文本: 为控制菜价，国务院办公厅于19日发通知，要求免征蔬菜流通环节增值税。
翻译版: In order to control the vegetable price, the General Office of the State Council issued a notice on the 19th, requiring the exemption of vegetable circulation VAT.
判断依据: 控制菜价、免征蔬菜流通环节增值税

文本: 在储备期内如果出现某种蔬菜涨幅较大的情况，可对该品种蔬菜进行临时价格干预。
翻译版: In the reserve period if there is a certain increase in the situation of vegetables, the varieties of vegetables can be temporary price intervention.
判断依据: 蔬菜涨幅较大的情况、价格干预

文本: 2010年，各地区、各部门按照党中央、国务院关于处理好保持经济平稳较快发展、调整经济结构和管理通胀预期关系的要求，积极采取措施，管理预期、发展生产、保障供应、强化监管，价格调控监管工作取得了积极成效。12月份，鲜菜价格环比下降9.4%，降幅比上月加大7.5个百分点
翻译版: In 2010, all localities and departments in accordance with the requirements of the CPC Central Committee and the State Council on handling the steady and rapid economic development, adjusting the economic structure and managing inflation expectations, and actively take measures to manage expectations, develop production, protect supply, strengthen supervision, Price regulation and control work has achieved positive results. In December, fresh vegetables prices fell 9.4% qoq, an increase of 7.5 percentage points over the previous month
判断依据: 管理通胀预期关系的要求、鲜菜价格环比下降

文本: 在“晋12条”政策保障下，我省物价调控组合拳正在发挥作用，以蔬菜食品为主的日用必需品价格正在逐渐平稳，部分商品开始回落走低，普通百姓特别是困难群众的生活压力有所减轻，相信在政府的有力措施保障下，百姓的“米袋子”和“菜篮子”将不再会成为难题。
翻译版: In the "Jin 12" policy protection, the province price regulation and control boxing boxing is playing a role, mainly to vegetable food and daily necessities prices are gradually stable, some commodities began to fall lower, ordinary people, especially the difficulties of the masses of life pressure By the government's strong measures to protect the people's "rice bag" and "basket" will no longer be a problem.
判断依据: 物价调控、蔬菜食品、回落走低

文本: 去年菜价高，伊犁州直各级政府积极应对，采取了一系列平抑物价的措施，保证百姓菜篮子。
翻译版: Last year, high prices of vegetables, Yili state direct government at all levels to respond, to take a series of measures to stabilize prices to ensure that people basket.
判断依据: 平抑物价、菜篮子

文本: 国家统计局近日公布我国10月宏观经济数据，居民消费指数同比上涨4.4%，其中食品类价格上涨10.1%，蔬菜价格涨了31%，创两年来的新高。由于受国际和国内市场的多重因素影响，防控通货膨胀可能是我国当前宏观经济调控面临的最大问题。在流动性充裕和通胀预期较强背景下，要加强通货膨胀预期的管理，通过内外并举，两拳出击，切实缓解物价持续上涨的问题。
翻译版: National Bureau of Statistics recently released China's macroeconomic data in October, the consumer index rose 4.4%, of which food prices rose 10.1%, vegetable prices rose 31%, a two-year high. Due to the multiple factors of international and domestic market, prevention and control of inflation may be the biggest problem facing China's current macroeconomic regulation and control. In the context of strong liquidity and strong inflation expectations, to strengthen the management of inflation expectations, both inside and outside, fists, and effectively alleviate the problem of rising prices.
判断依据: 蔬菜价格、防控通货膨胀、缓解物价持续上涨

文本: 已拿出150万元补贴“菜篮子”，目前，全市共建成农副产品平价商店8家。据市物价局的价格监测显示：平价商店同质农副产品价格普遍低于市场平均价10%以上，群众习惯消费的蔬菜价格低于市场平均价格20%左右。
翻译版: Has come up with 1.5 million yuan subsidy "vegetable basket", at present, the city built a total of eight agricultural and sideline products parity stores. According to the price monitoring of the City Price Bureau shows: parity stores homogeneous agricultural and sideline products prices generally lower than the market average price of more than 10%, the masses used to consume vegetable prices below the market average price of about 20%.
判断依据: 150万元补贴“菜篮子”、蔬菜价格低于市场平均价格

文本: 乌鲁木齐自从2010年开始探索建立社区蔬菜副食品直销点（俗称平价菜店）以来，通过剔除中间环节，使得菜价平均下降20%，对平抑菜价起到了重要作用。
翻译版: Urumqi since 2010 began to explore the establishment of community direct sales of vegetable non-staple food (commonly known as the price of food shop), through the elimination of intermediate links, making the average price of vegetables decreased by 20%, played an important role in stabilizing the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 蔬菜副食品直销点、剔除中间环节、菜价平均下降

文本: 记者从西安市商务局获悉，本月和下月，西安将分两阶段投放政府储备菜，价格低于市场零售价10%至15%，有效应对节假日来临引起的蔬菜市场价格异常波动，提高节日蔬菜应急保障能力。
翻译版: Reporters learned from the Xi'an Municipal Bureau of Commerce, this month and next month, Xi'an will be divided into two stages of government food, the price is lower than the market retail price of 10% to 15%, effectively deal with the holiday market caused by abnormal fluctuations in vegetable prices, Vegetable emergency support capability.
判断依据: 储备菜、价格低于市场零售价

文本: 针对近期国内蔬菜价格持续上涨，为控制源头蔬菜价格，保障北京市冬季蔬菜市场供应，从1月26日19时起，市政府决定在新发地农副产品批发市场实施8种蔬菜入场费减免。新发地批发市场也同期对出场运输车辆免收出场费，其经营的121个直营菜店销售的8种蔬菜价格也将同步下降。
翻译版: In view of the recent rise in domestic vegetable prices, in order to control the source of vegetable prices to protect the supply of vegetables in Beijing winter market, from January 26 onwards 19:00, the city government decided to new agricultural and sideline products wholesale market implementation of eight kinds of vegetable entrance fee relief The The new wholesale market is also the same period on the appearance of transport vehicles to avoid the appearance fee, the operation of the 121 direct sales of the eight vegetable prices will also be synchronized.
判断依据: 蔬菜入场费减免、蔬菜价格也将同步下降
来源: 北京市发展改革委网站

文本: 在去年9月份玉米马上要收获的时候，中央出台了新的玉米临储价格，价格差不多降了二成多
翻译版: In September last year when the corn to be harvested, the central government introduced a new corn temporary storage prices, the price almost reduced by more than two percent
判断依据: 玉米临储价格、价格差不多降了二成多

文本: 佛山市发改局局长何国森表示，稳定价格最主要是有有效的价格调控措施，开展平价商店建设，通过鼓励产销对接，减少流通环节、降低流通成本，最终降低零售价格起到价格示范作用。
翻译版: Foshan City Development and Reform Bureau Director He Guosen said that the most stable price is effective price control measures to carry out the construction of parity stores, by encouraging production and marketing docking, reduce circulation, reduce the cost of circulation, and ultimately reduce the retail price play a role model.
判断依据: 稳定价格、减少流通环节

文本: 连日来，省委、省政府高度重视物价问题，为稳定市场物价和保障群众基本生活，采取了多项措施，目前，西宁市蔬菜价格呈现稳中有降的态势。海湖路工商所副所长周育红告诉记者，目前海湖路农副产品批发市场蔬菜品种多，货源充足，价格稳定，而且辣子、笋子、甘蓝、白菜的价格相对九月中旬每斤下降了2毛到3毛。
翻译版: In recent days, the provincial government attaches great importance to the issue price, to stabilize market prices and protect the basic living, has taken a number of measures, at present, Xining vegetable prices showed a flat to down trend. Wu Hai, deputy director of Industry and Commerce Zhou Yu-hong told reporters that Wu Hai agricultural products wholesale vegetable varieties, adequate supply, price stability, and Spicy, bamboo shoots, cabbage, Chinese cabbage prices relative to mid-September fell by 2 per catty Hair to 3 hairs.
判断依据: 稳定市场物价、蔬菜价格、稳重有降

文本: 值得一提的是，节日期间，市政府对全市蔬菜市场供应实施阶段性政策调控，以蔬菜中心批发市场为载体，对入场业户减免一切费用，市场应收费用由市政府拨付。春节前全市生猪最高日上市量达6052头，蔬菜最高日登市量为3400吨。蔬菜批发价格总体下降
翻译版: It is worth mentioning that during the holiday season, the municipal government on the city's vegetable market supply and implementation of the stage of policy control to the vegetable market wholesale market as the carrier, the entrance business households to reduce all costs, the market charges paid by the municipal government. Before the Spring Festival, the highest number of live pigs in the city reached 6052, the highest daily market for vegetables is 3400 tons. Vegetable wholesale prices overall decline
判断依据: 政策调控、以蔬菜中心批发市场为载体、蔬菜批发价格总体下降

文本: 当前蔬菜价格急速回落，一是由于本地蔬菜大量上市，供应量增加，二是因为政府宏观调控的政策效应。根据《国务院关于稳定消费价格总水平保障群众基本生活的通知》（国发[2010]40号）精神，11月22日市政府常务会议出台了确保市场供应的8条措施，有关部门降低了超市和农贸市场的摊位费、进场费，各大超 市直接与产地对接，减少流通环节，一些超市还开辟了“一元菜”、特价菜专区。
翻译版: The current rapid decline in vegetable prices, first, due to a large number of local vegetables listed, the supply increased, and second, because the government's macro-control policy effect. According to the "State Council on the stability of the overall level of consumer prices to protect the basic livelihood of the notice" (Guo Fa [2010] 40) spirit, November 22 municipal government executive meeting to ensure that the market supply of eight measures, the relevant departments to reduce the supermarket And farmers market stalls, entry fees, the major supermarkets directly with the origin of docking, reduce circulation, some supermarkets also opened up a "yuan dish", special food area.
判断依据: 蔬菜价格急速回落、降低了超市和农贸市场的摊位费、进场费

文本: 为应对菜价不断上涨，海口市政府5日上午发布公告，从即日起到春节假期，紧急动用价格调节基金实施调控，在全市26家农贸市场、6家超市、48家平价商店(专区)共80个平价菜供应点，对8种蔬菜实行不限量平价销售。
翻译版: In response to the rising prices of vegetables, Haikou municipal government issued a notice on the 5th morning, from now on to the Spring Festival holiday, emergency use of price adjustment fund to implement regulation and control, in the city's 26 farmers market, six supermarkets, 48 parity stores (area) 80 parity vegetable supply point, the implementation of eight kinds of vegetables are not limited parity sales.
判断依据: 为应对菜价不断上涨、菜实行不限量平价销售

文本: “陕九条”的相关举措中，对运输鲜活农产品（000061）车辆免收车辆通行费，成为最引人关注的一点。陕西省希望通过这种方式来降低农产品运输成本，进而平抑菜价。
翻译版: Shaanxi nine related initiatives, the transport of fresh agricultural products (000061) vehicles free of vehicle toll, become the most interesting point. Shaanxi Province in this way to reduce the cost of agricultural transport, and thus stabilize the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 鲜活农产品、免收车辆通行费、平抑菜价

文本: 记者12日从武汉市农委获悉，为确保菜篮子保供稳价，武汉启动蔬菜“补贴限价销售”，在150个超市实行限价销售，每个品种每斤限价1元，大多数蔬菜价格均有回落。
翻译版: Reporters on the 12th from the Wuhan City Agricultural Commission was informed that in order to ensure that the basket of vegetables for the stable price, Wuhan start vegetables "subsidy price sales", in 150 supermarkets to limit the sale of sales, each species price of 1 yuan per catty, most vegetables Prices are down.
对应指标: 补贴、价格价格上限的直接定价
判断依据: 补贴限价销售、蔬菜价格均有回落

文本: “十块钱买不了多少菜”，这几年不少中国城市居民都面临这样的烦恼。然而，今年５月份以来，山西省太原在全市开展“每日四种蔬菜一元钱”活动（以下简称“一元菜”），使频频“发烧”的菜价明显降温。
翻译版: Ten dollars can not buy how many dishes, a few years many Chinese urban residents are faced with such trouble. However, since May this year, Taiyuan, Shanxi Province in the city to carry out the "four daily vegetables a dollar" activities (hereinafter referred to as "one yuan dish"), so frequently "fever" vegetable prices significantly cool.
判断依据: 一元菜、菜价明显降温

文本: 今年的中央经济工作会议提出，要全面加强价格调控监管工作，保持物价总水平基本稳定。而稳定物价，也是政府部门这段时间来最重要的任务。最近，国家发改委等部门就对山西、江苏、天津等地的物价工作进行了督察，而商务部昨天发布的监测也显示，蔬菜价格已经连续下降了五周。
翻译版: This year's central economic work conference proposed to fully strengthen the regulation of price regulation and control, to maintain the overall level of price stability. And stable prices, but also the government sector this time to the most important task. Recently, the National Development and Reform Commission and other departments on the Shanxi, Jiangsu, Tianjin and other places of the price of the work of the inspectors, and the Ministry of Commerce yesterday released monitoring also showed that vegetable prices have been declining for five weeks.
判断依据: 格调控监管工作、蔬菜价格、下降了五周

文本: 作为一项惠民工程，果蔬店从“新鲜、便利、低价、安全”等方面着手让老百姓得实惠和方便。“店里80%的蔬菜直接采自农民菜地，实现了从田间地头到市民餐桌的一步到位，中间流通环节大大减少，有效降低了蔬菜价格。
翻译版: As a Huimin project, fruit and vegetable shop from the "fresh, convenient, cheap, safe," and so on to let people get benefits and convenience. "80% of the vegetables in the shop directly from the farmers vegetable land, from the field to the public to the table one step in the middle of the circulation is greatly reduced, effectively reducing the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 蔬菜直接采自农民菜地、中间流通环节大大减少、有效降低了蔬菜价格

文本: 在市场价格大幅上涨或较为平稳时，平价蔬菜、水果类销售价格原则应低于当地同类市场均价15%以上，粮油肉禽蛋及其他生活必需品价格原则上应低于市场均价5%以上。原因就在于政府将从价格调节基金中，安排一部分专项资金给予商店租金补贴或贷款补贴等。
翻译版: In the market prices rose sharply or more stable, the price of cheap vegetables, fruit sales price should be lower than the local average price of more than 15% of similar markets, grain and poultry eggs and other necessities in principle, the price should be lower than the market average price of more than 5% The The reason is that the government will arrange some of the special funds from the price adjustment fund to give the store rent subsidies or loan subsidies.
判断依据: 低于、补贴

文本: 今年政府补贴蔬菜的控价效果非常明显，以白菜、土豆、芹菜、胡萝卜、葱头为主打的大陆菜，其销售价格基本平稳，且略有下降，降幅在7%左右。
翻译版: This year the government subsidy vegetables control effect is very obvious, to cabbage, potatoes, celery, carrots, onions hit the mainland dishes, the sales price is basically stable, and a slight decline, down about 7%.
判断依据: 补贴、略有下降

文本: 西宁市商务局市场监测监管处处长王国平说：“实施限价补贴是为了让老百姓在节前能够吃得起、吃得好，价格降低了，百姓餐桌上菜品更丰富了，才能踏踏实实过好年。”
翻译版: Xining City Bureau of Commerce Market Supervision and Supervision Director Wang Guoping said: "The implementation of the limit subsidy is to allow people to eat before the holiday, eat well, the price is reduced, the people on the table more richer dishes, It was a good year.
判断依据: 补贴、价格降低

文本: 福州10日开始对大白菜、上海青、豆芽菜和空心菜等4种主要蔬菜实施“限价令”。至11日，福州永辉、新华都等6家主要超市的80家门店全部将菜价调至政府指导价之下，4种大路菜的降价幅度两日间普遍达到15%—50%。
翻译版: Fuzhou 10 days on the cabbage, Shanghai green, bean sprouts and water spinach and other four kinds of vegetables to implement the "limit order." To 11, Fuzhou Yonghui, Xinhua and other six major supermarkets, 80 stores will be transferred to the government under the guidance of the price under the guidance of the four kinds of road prices in the two days between the general rate of 15% -50%.
判断依据: 指导价、降价

文本: 在降低批发环节运营成本方面，按照福州政府的要求，各蔬菜批发市场将采取措施降低商户经营成本，当蔬菜混合平均价高于3元/公斤时，市场免收5%管理费。
翻译版: In reducing the operating costs of the wholesale sector, in accordance with the requirements of the Fuzhou government, the vegetable wholesale market will take measures to reduce business costs, when the average price of vegetables mixed with more than 3 yuan / kg, the market free of 5% management fee.
判断依据: 降低、运营成本

文本: 省物价局介绍，政府发补贴，目的也是为了让平价店更好地为居民服务。但是，要想拿到这笔钱，要求是非常严格的。平价店每天必须为市民提供15种以上的平价蔬菜，每种蔬菜的价格必须低于全市均价15%。
翻译版: Provincial Price Bureau, the government issued a subsidy, the purpose is to allow parity shop to better serve the residents. However, in order to get the money, the request is very strict. The parity shop must provide the public with more than 15 kinds of cheap vegetables every day. The price of each vegetable must be less than 15% of the city's average price.
判断依据: 补贴、价格低于

文本: 上海静安区内的每个菜市场每天都要设置一个平价菜供应摊位，以低于市场价15%-20%的价格对外销售，由区政府安排专项资金，对平价摊位给予补贴。
翻译版: Shanghai Jing'an District, every vegetable market every day to set a parity supply booth, to the market price of 15% -20% of the price of foreign sales by the district government to arrange special funds to subsidize parity booths.
判断依据: 低于市场价、补贴

文本: 依托现有平价商店，启动2016年第二期政府差价补贴销售蔬菜机制（具体品种详见下表）。每日蔬菜销售价格以我委通知的协议价执行(即:以市发改委成本监审局提供的数据为依据,低于同类市场均价15%，具体价格另行通知)。
翻译版: Relying on the existing parity store, start the second phase of the 2016 government subsidy sales vegetable mechanism (see the table below for specific varieties). Daily vegetable sales price to the Commission to inform the implementation of the agreement price (ie: the Municipal Development and Reform Commission to provide the cost of the Bureau of the data, based on lower than the average market price of 15%, the specific price of another notice).
判断依据: 补贴、低于、均价
来源: 厦门市发展和改革委员会

文本: 在超市开设平价蔬菜柜台，补贴这些柜台的装修和租金，条件只有一个，每天提供15种低于市场价格15%的蔬菜，保证供应。
翻译版: In the supermarket to open an affordable vegetable counter, subsidize the decoration and rent of these counters, only one condition, providing 15 kinds of vegetables below 15% of the market price, to ensure supply.
判断依据: 补贴、低于市场价格

文本: 全市立即启动蔬菜“补贴限价销售”。先期连续10天对包菜、土豆、大白菜、冬瓜四个品种，在150个超市实行限价销售，每个品种每斤限价1元，日上市45万公斤，占全市蔬菜消费量的10%。
翻译版: The city immediately start the vegetable "subsidy price sales." 10 consecutive days on the cabbage, potatoes, cabbage, melon four varieties, 150 supermarkets in the implementation of the limit sales, each price of 1 yuan per catty, listed on the 450,000 kilograms, accounting for the city's vegetable consumption of 10 %.
判断依据: 限价销售

文本: 是我省省级财政补贴肉菜投放市场进行销售的第一天。上午9时，记者赶到北国超市益东店，这里已经是人流如梭了。蔬菜品种丰富也很新鲜，购买的市民非常踊跃。"这里大白菜、土豆、胡萝卜的价格感觉比菜市场还要便宜些
翻译版: Is the province's provincial financial subsidies to sell meat market on the first day of sales. 9:00 am, the reporter rushed to the North supermarket Yidong shop, where it is already flown. Variety of vegetables is also very fresh, very popular to buy the public. "Here the price of cabbage, potatoes, carrots feel cheaper than the vegetable market even more
判断依据: 补贴、蔬菜、便宜

文本: 福州10日开始对大白菜、上海青、豆芽菜和空心菜等4种主要蔬菜实施“限价令”。至11日，福州永辉、新华都（002264）等6家主要超市的80家门店全部将菜价调至政府指导价之下，4种大路菜的降价幅度两日间普遍达到15％—50％。
翻译版: Fuzhou 10 days on the cabbage, Shanghai green, bean sprouts and water spinach and other four kinds of vegetables to implement the "limit order." To 11, Fuzhou Yonghui, Xinhua (002264) and other six major supermarkets, 80 stores will be transferred to the government under the guidance of the price under the guidance of four kinds of road prices in the two days between the general rate of 15% -50 %.
判断依据: 限价令、降价

文本: 石景山区商务委工作人员多次与超市方沟通，并给予资金支持。多方努力下，本月初才使得永辉超市这处占地20余平方米的蔬菜专区开张了。政府扶持平价菜销售专区，专门平价甚至亏本卖菜。
翻译版: Shijingshan District Commercial Committee staff to communicate with the supermarket several times, and to give financial support. Multi-party efforts, this month makes Yonghui supermarket here covers an area of ​​20 square meters of vegetable area opened. The government to support parity vegetable sales area, special parity or even loss of selling vegetables. In the case of
判断依据: 资金支持、亏本卖菜

文本: 在永辉、新华都(21.42，-0.07，-0.33%)、蓝天、兴福兴、万嘉五大本土超市旗下的70多个店面，对空心菜、上海青、大白菜、豆芽等四类大宗菜实施销售协商价，上限依次为（每500g）1.9元、1.5元、1.3元、1元，菜价应声而落。在本土主流超市，菜价重回1元时代。
翻译版: In the Yonghui, Xinhua are, blue sky, Xing Fuxing, Wanjia five local supermarkets more than 70 stores, on the spinach, Shanghai green, Chinese cabbage, bean sprouts and other four kinds of large dishes The implementation of the sale of the consultation price, the upper limit in order (per 500g) 1.9 yuan, 1.5 yuan, 1.3 yuan, 1 yuan, vegetable prices and fall. In the mainstream supermarket, vegetable prices back to 1 yuan era.
判断依据: 上限、应声回落

文本: 3月份以来，北京菜价坐上了“过山车”，开始扶摇直上，鲁安平的直通车上也贴上了“限价蔬菜单”，每次以上货的批发价售卖蔬菜。
翻译版: Since March, Beijing vegetable prices got on the "roller coaster", began to skyrocket, Lu Anping through train also posted a "limit the price of vegetables," each time the wholesale price of goods sold vegetables.
判断依据: 限价、批发价

文本: 11月19日，兰州市开始向城关、七里河、安宁、西固四区的96家蔬菜直销店投放总量约720吨的"1元菜"品种为土豆、大白菜、胡萝卜。与此同时，每个蔬菜直销店还将有7种限价蔬菜按照低于市场价15%的价格销售，品种分别为绿萝卜、洋葱、莲花菜、白萝卜、青笋、茄王、圆茄。
翻译版: November 19, Lanzhou City began to Chengguan, Qilihe, Anning, Xigu four districts of 96 vegetable outlets to put a total of about 720 tons of "1 yuan dish" varieties of potatoes, cabbage, carrots. At the same time, each vegetable outlet will have seven kinds of price of vegetables in accordance with the market price of less than 15% of the price, the varieties were green radish, onion, lotus, white radish, green bamboo shoots, Solanum, The In the case of
判断依据: 限价、低于市场价

文本: 目前向各蔬菜直销点可配送80多个蔬菜品种，覆盖了98%以上的蔬菜品种，其中25个品种实行限价销售。
翻译版: At present, direct sales of vegetables to more than 80 varieties of vegetables, covering more than 98% of the varieties of vegetables, of which 25 varieties of restrictions on sales.
判断依据: 限价

文本: 近日福州发布蔬菜限价令，成为中国第一个政府干预、控制菜价的城市，叶菜价格控制在两块以内。今天本报热线接到一些市民的电话，表示希望海南也采取相应措施干预菜价。
翻译版: Recently, Fuzhou issued a vegetable price order to become China's first government intervention, control the price of the city, leafy vegetables control in less than two. Today, the newspaper hotline received a number of public telephone, expressed the hope that Hainan also take the appropriate measures to intervene in vegetable prices.
判断依据: 限价令

文本: 近日，财政部、国税总局联合发文，决定从2012年1月1日起，将免征蔬菜流通环节增值税，此次减免税目录涉及14个类别219个品种的蔬菜。为贯彻执行好此项惠民政策，国税局采取多项措施，确保政策执行到位。
翻译版: Recently, the Ministry of Finance, the State Administration of Taxation jointly issued a document, decided from January 1, 2012 onwards, will be exempt from the flow of vegetables value-added tax, the tax relief directory covers 14 categories of 219 varieties of vegetables. In order to implement the Huimin policy, the IRS has taken a number of measures to ensure that policy implementation is in place.
判断依据: 流通环节

文本: 市财政局从价调基金中安排部分资金对西宁农商公司蔬菜调运费和平价销售店进行适当补贴，实现平价菜店蔬菜销售价格低于市场价格10%的目标。
翻译版: City Finance Bureau from the price of funds to arrange part of the funds on the Xining Agricultural Company vegetable freight and cheap sales of appropriate subsidies to achieve parity vegetable vegetable sales price is lower than the market price of 10% target.
判断依据: 补贴、价格低于
来源: 商务部驻西安特派员办事处

文本: 乌鲁木齐市现有的450个社区蔬菜副食品直销点正式实施社区蔬菜副食品直销点销售的所有蔬菜，在一级蔬菜批发市场净重价格基础上加价幅度不超过10%的政策，若不执行市民可根据直销点公布的举报电话举报。
翻译版: Urumqi City, the existing 450 community direct sales of vegetables and non-staple food directly to the implementation of community vegetables, direct sales of all vegetables vegetables, in a vegetable wholesale market, based on the net price increase rate of not more than 10% of the policy, if not the implementation of the public According to the direct point of publication of the reported phone call.
判断依据: 加价幅度

文本: 统一调运上述蔬菜品种，按照协商批发价供应给大型超市和平价商店，超市和平价商店以协商零售价进行销售，实际采购价与协商批发价之间的差价由福州市财政补贴。
翻译版: Unified delivery of the above-mentioned vegetable varieties, in accordance with the agreed wholesale price supply to large supermarkets and parity stores, supermarkets and parity stores to negotiate the retail price of sales, the actual purchase price and consultation between the wholesale price difference by the Fuzhou financial subsidies.
判断依据: 补贴

文本: 同时，降低农产品批发市场、农贸市场、社区市场摊位费收费标准，并给予租户减免相关税费等优惠政策，对蔬菜品种实施价格补贴，在蔬菜流通过程中收取的其他费用，按照最低收费标准，尽量少收或免收，力争通过降低运输和经营成本降低蔬菜价格。
翻译版: At the same time, reduce the wholesale market of agricultural products, farmers market, community market booth fee charges, and give tenants relief related taxes and other preferential policies, the implementation of price subsidies for vegetable varieties in the process of vegetable circulation fees charged in accordance with the minimum fees, As far as possible less or free, and strive to reduce the transport and operating costs to reduce the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 补贴、降低蔬菜价格

文本: 统一调运调控的蔬菜品种，按照协商批发价供应给大型超市和平价商店，超市和平价商店以协商零售价进行销售，实际采购价与协商批发价之间的差价，由市财政给予补贴。
翻译版: The varieties of vegetables regulated by the unified regulation and control shall be supplied to large supermarkets and parity stores, supermarkets and parity stores at the negotiated wholesale price for sale at the negotiated retail price. The difference between the actual purchase price and the agreed wholesale price shall be subsidized by the municipal finance.
判断依据: 补贴

文本: 武汉市还将适时启动蔬菜“限价销售”。为了保障城镇居民的消费需求、降低生活成本，武汉市农委已制定了蔬菜“限价销售”紧急预案，并启动了监测预警机制，一旦蔬菜价格产生大幅异动，将适时在全市大型超市启动蔬菜“限价销售”工作。
翻译版: Wuhan City will also start the timely vegetable "limit sales." In order to protect the consumption needs of urban residents and reduce the cost of living, Wuhan Agricultural Commission has developed a "limit sales" emergency plan, and launched a monitoring and early warning mechanism, once the price of vegetables have changed, will be timely in the city's large supermarkets to start vegetables "Limit sales" work.
判断依据: 限价销售

文本: 在超市开设平价蔬菜柜台，补贴这些柜台的装修和租金，条件只有一个，每天提供15种低于市场价格15%的蔬菜
翻译版: In the supermarket to open an affordable vegetable counter, subsidize the decoration and rental of these counters, the conditions are only one day to provide 15 below 15% of the market price of vegetables
判断依据: 补贴、低于市场价格

文本: 记者12日从武汉市农委获悉，为确保菜篮子保供稳价，武汉启动蔬菜“补贴限价销售”，在150个超市实行限价销售，每个品种每斤限价1元，大多数蔬菜价格均有回落。
翻译版: 12, reporters learned from wuhan agriculture commission, in order to ensure the basket for stabilizing price, wuhan start vegetables "subsidies limit sales", in 150 the supermarket price sale, each variety price 1 yuan per kilogram, most of the vegetable prices have dropped.
判断依据: 限价，回落

文本: 为保障福州市市场供应，稳定蔬菜价格，在保证菜农、超市利润的前提下，福州已启动蔬菜价格协商机制。经与财政局、物价局等部门充分协商，对调控蔬菜的协商批发价和零售价达成一致意见。统一调运上述蔬菜品种，按照协商批发价供应给大型超市和平价商店，超市和平价商店以协商零售价进行销售，实际采购价与协商批发价之间的差价由福州市财政补贴。购补贴品种蔬菜实惠。
翻译版: In order to guarantee the supply of fuzhou market and stabilize vegetable prices, fuzhou has started the vegetable price negotiation mechanism under the premise of ensuring the profit of vegetable farmers and supermarkets. Through consultation with the finance bureau and the price bureau, we reached an agreement on the wholesale price and retail price of vegetables. The vegetable varieties, unified dispatching according to negotiate wholesale supply large supermarkets and grocery stores, supermarkets and grocery stores to negotiate the retail price to sell, the actual purchase price and negotiate wholesale price difference between the fuzhou subsidies. Subsidized varieties of vegetables are affordable.
判断依据: 实惠，补贴

文本: 公益性菜场所以生鲜，不能高于批发价的30%出售，也就是说，1元批发的蔬菜，只能卖1.3元以下，不能超过1.3克。到2016年年底使全市蔬菜等主要“菜篮子”商品价格在现有菜价的基础上平均下降10%。
翻译版: The public welfare vegetable field is fresh, can't be higher than the wholesale price 30% sale, namely, 1 yuan wholesale vegetables, can only sell 1.3 yuan below, cannot exceed 1.3 grams. By the end of 2016, the prices of major "vegetable baskets" such as vegetables in the city were reduced by an average of 10 percent on the basis of existing prices.
判断依据: 不能高于，下降

文本: 河北省惠民补贴肉菜开售 菜价便宜20%。此次惠民补贴销售由全省47家规模大、信誉好的大型商超承担，以低于市场20%的价格补贴销售蔬菜，以每市斤低于市场1元和4元的价格补贴销售猪肉和牛羊肉。
翻译版: Huimin in hebei province subsidized meat dishes to sell at a 20% discount. The huimin subsidies sales by the province's 47 large scale and good reputation of large business super, of selling vegetables, below 20% of the market price subsidies of $1 and $4 per jin is lower than the market price subsidies selling pork and beef and mutton.
判断依据: 补贴，便宜

文本: 这次补贴的平价蔬菜包括米苋、鸡毛菜、青菜、生菜、卷心菜和芹菜6种。与其它摊头相比，这里的6种菜平均便宜20%到40%不等。
翻译版: The subsidized price of vegetables including amaranth, chicken, green vegetables, lettuce, cabbage and celery. Compared with other vendors, the average six dishes here are 20 percent to 40 percent cheaper.
判断依据: 补贴，便宜

文本: 2012年，内蒙古呼和浩特市市级财政投入2.5亿元，对新建的(一亩标准)高效日光温室最高给予3万元的补贴，扶持农民建成3.3万亩蔬菜保护基地，在增加农民收入的同时，有效降低菜价，丰富市民“菜篮子”。
翻译版: In 2012, Inner Mongolia Hohhot city financial investment 250 million yuan, (one mu standards) of new high efficiency highest 30000 yuan in subsidies for the sunlight greenhouse, supporting farmers built 33000 mu of vegetable protection base, at the same time of increasing farmers' income, effectively reduce the price, rich people "vegetable basket".
判断依据: 补贴，降低菜价

文本: 据介绍，政府对平价商店实施税费减免政策并给予补贴，以保障其农副产品的供应。使用价格调节基金对平价商店的房租租赁费用、配送车辆运行费用、蔬菜生产基地建设等进行补贴，每经营满一年发放一次。当市场价格大幅上涨或较为平稳时，平价商店要有不少于15个品种的蔬菜销售价格低于周边市场15%以上，每天还要推出不少于5个品种的1元菜，粮、油、肉、禽、蛋以及其他生活必需品价格原则上应低于同类市场均价5%以上。
翻译版: According to the introduction, the government has implemented tax breaks and subsidies for the affordable stores to guarantee the supply of their agricultural and sideline products. The price adjustment fund is used to subsidize the rent and rent of the affordable stores, the running costs of the vehicles and the construction of vegetable production bases, etc., which are distributed once a year. When the market price rose sharply or stable, cheap grocery stores have not less than 15 varieties of vegetables more than 15% of the sales price is lower than the surrounding market, also launched a day not less than 1 yuan 5 varieties of food, grain, oil, meat, poultry, eggs and other necessities price should be lower than the same kind in principle the market average price of more than 5%.
判断依据: 补贴，价格低于

文本: 从去年9月，市政府针对农民“卖菜难”和城市居民“买菜贵”的矛盾，从降低“菜园子”到“菜篮子”的流通成本入手，启动了产销对接、惠民蔬菜直销工程，从根本上减少了蔬菜流通环节、降低了终端市场上的蔬菜价格，让利于民。
翻译版: Since last September, the city government for farmers and urban residents "difficult to selling vegetables" contradiction "buy your dishes", "garden" to the circulation cost of "vegetable basket", start the production and marketing docking, huimin vegetables direct engineering, radically reduce the vegetables circulation, reduces the terminals on the market prices of vegetables, benefiting the people.
判断依据: 减少了蔬菜流通环节，降低了蔬菜价格

文本: 据悉，平价超市经营的肉、蛋、禽类价格必须低于市场价5%，蔬菜价格低于市场价20%，并标明当天市场的对比价格。每个店每年将获得政府价格调节基金补贴1.2万元。
翻译版: The price of meat, eggs and poultry sold at the affordable market must be below 5 percent of the market price, vegetables are 20 percent below the market price and the price of the market is marked on the same day. Each store will receive a government price adjustment fund of 12,000 yuan per year.
判断依据: 低于市场，补贴

文本: 昨日是我市对12个品种蔬菜实行价调基金补贴的第一天，双兴蔬菜批发市场明显比前一阵热闹许多。早上6时多记者赶到市场时，这里已被各地涌来的大中型运菜车挤得水泄不通。随着价调基金政策的启动，部分蔬菜批发价格已出现微降。
翻译版: Yesterday was the first day of subsidies for 12 varieties of vegetables in our city, and the wholesale vegetable market was much more lively than before. When reporters arrived at the market at 6:00 a.m., it was crowded with large and medium-sized truckloads. With the start of the policy of price adjustment, some wholesale vegetable prices have been slightly reduced.
判断依据: 基金补贴，微降

文本: 为了平稳蔬菜价格，长春市政府紧急出台四项措施，其中包括对长春蔬菜中心批发市场批发业户免收入场交易费、对经营大白菜、土豆两个品种的批发业户给予补贴等。昨日措施开始施行，从市场情况看，取得了一定的效果。才部长也表示，土豆和白菜的价格有明显的回落。
翻译版: To stable vegetable prices, changchun government introduced emergency four measures, including for changchun center of vegetables wholesale market wholesale business households, admission free transaction fees, for business Chinese cabbage, potatoes, two varieties subsidies and other wholesale business households. Yesterday's measures began to take effect, and from the market conditions, it achieved some results. The minister also said the price of potatoes and cabbage was down significantly.
判断依据: 补贴，回落

文本: 面对特殊天气及市场环境形成的菜价偏高现象，11月16日，双兴商品城决定在其机场前菜果批发市场实行“蔬菜双向补贴”，第一阶段试行期为七到十天。记者近日从各大市场了解到，这一双向政策补贴政策出台之后，零售市场相关品类蔬菜价格下降明显。
翻译版: Facing the special weather and market environment formation of the phenomenon of some inspections on the high side, on November 16, double hing commodity city vegetables fruit wholesale market before its airport to "vegetable two-way subsidy", the first stage of trial period for seven to ten days. Reporters recently learned from the big markets that the price of vegetables and vegetables in the retail market has fallen sharply after the policy was introduced.
判断依据: 蔬菜双向补贴，下降明显

文本: 1月15日,大连市发改委价格监督检查人员会同新闻单位对大连市蔬菜批发市场、大型商场、各大超市副食品供应及价格进行检查,结果表明:蔬菜价格有所回落,政府基金发挥重要作用,市场蔬菜品种齐全。
翻译版: Dalian municipal development and reform commission on January 15, the price supervision and inspection personnel in conjunction with the news media in dalian vegetable wholesale market, large shopping malls, supermarkets non-staple food supply and price check, the result showed that the vegetable prices fall, the government funds play an important role, market vegetable varieties complete.
判断依据: 回落，基金

文本: 让老百姓的菜篮拎得更轻松，黄浦区率先推行政府补贴企业行政事业管理费用的办法，适当减轻菜场经营成本，进一步缩小农副产品调价带来的影响。在寸土寸金的黄浦区，菜价却处于“低谷”，蔬菜价格比外区便宜10%-20%。
翻译版: Let people laden carry more easily, take the lead in implementing government subsidies of huangpu district enterprises administrative management fees, appropriate reduce operational costs of the market, further reducing the impact of the adjustment of agricultural and sideline products. In huangpu district, where the price is low, vegetable prices are at a "low point", and vegetable prices are 10% to 20% cheaper.
判断依据: 补贴，便宜

文本: 春节长假过后，随着批发、零售等蔬菜流通环节的恢复，蔬菜价格有所回落。
翻译版: After the Spring Festival holiday, vegetable prices retreated as wholesale, retail and other vegetable circulation links resumed.
判断依据: 流通环节的恢复，回落

文本: 北京采取多种模式减少蔬菜流通环节降低菜价
翻译版: Beijing has adopted a variety of models to reduce vegetable circulation and reduce vegetable prices
判断依据: 减少蔬菜流通环节，降低菜价

文本: 作为对去年税收减免政策的延续，此次对蔬菜流通环节的增值税免征，将在一定程度上降低蔬菜流通领域成本，进一步促使蔬菜零售价格下降，给广大消费者的菜篮子减负，使广大消费者真正受益。
翻译版: As to the continuation of last year's tax cuts, the value-added tax shall be exempted in the vegetable circulation, the will to a certain extent, reduced cost of vegetable circulation, prompted vegetable retail prices fall further, to the vast number of consumers of basket and burden, make broad consumer real benefit.
判断依据: 流通环节的增值税免征，价格下降

文本: 记者昨日从市国税局了解到，根据财政部、国家税务总局规定，自今年1月1日起，国家对蔬菜流通环节免征增值税。此项政策的出台将在一定程度上降低蔬菜流通领域成本，给“菜篮子”减负，让消费者受益。
翻译版: Yesterday, the reporter learned from the city's internal revenue service that, according to the ministry of finance and the state administration of taxation, the state has exempted the VAT on vegetable circulation from January 1 this year. This policy will reduce the cost of vegetable circulation to a certain extent, and the "vegetable basket" will be reduced and consumers will benefit.
判断依据: 免征增值税，减负，受益

文本: 目前，武汉启动蔬菜“补贴限价销售”，记者采访多家蔬菜市场摊贩后发现，大多数蔬菜价格均有回落。
翻译版: At present, wuhan starts the vegetable "subsidy limit sale", the reporter interviewed many vegetable market stalls and found that most vegetable prices have come down.
判断依据: 限价销售，回落

文本: 首府从11月6日才开始实施蔬菜直销点所有菜限价销售措施，但一周来，各区县的蔬菜直销点管理部门都采取了相应的措施，让市民感觉到直销点“变了样”，进入直销店的顾客都发现，如今来买菜，蔬菜直销点的菜品新鲜了，价格降低了，工作人员的笑容也多了。
翻译版: Capital from November 6th to vegetables outlets all food price sales measures, but in a week, each district and county of vegetables outlets are adopted corresponding measures, the administrative department to make citizens feel outlets "changed", customers into stores found that now to buy food, food fresh vegetables outlets, the price is reduced, the staff smile too much.
判断依据: 限价销售，价格降低

文本: 昨日，首先尝试蔬菜“零售限价”模式的朝阳农贸市场亮出成绩单，两个月来销量由此前的每日60吨上升到80吨，销量增弥补了蔬菜零售价降低后摊贩失去的毛利润,而这部分让利又让市民菜篮子变得更稳更轻。
翻译版: Yesterday, first try to vegetables "retail price" model of chaoyang farmers market with transcripts, two months before the daily sales rose 60 tons to 80 tons, sales increase makes up for the vegetable retail price lower gross margins vendors after losing, and this part of the benefit and make citizens basket more lighter.
判断依据: 零售限价，菜篮子变得更稳更轻

文本: 辽宁朝阳市农贸市场实施了“蔬菜限价令”，在全国同业中率先核定蔬菜批零毛利后实行限价销售，对价格进行适当干预，减轻市民的菜篮子，把‘最后一公里’的高菜价压下来，市场上蔬菜价跌量升，形成良性循环后，菜贩收益有增无减。
翻译版: Liaoning chaoyang farmers market implemented the "vegetable price", in the national trade pioneered check and ratify the vegetables zero margin and the sales price, the price appropriate intervention, reduce citizens' basket, and the "last mile" high price, quantity of vegetables on the market price falls, forming a virtuous cycle, greengrocer earnings increase.
判断依据: 蔬菜限价令，蔬菜价跌

文本: 蔬菜售卖减少了流通环节，可以降低蔬菜的价格，同时，通过信息平台的建立，直销直供的蔬菜还将制定最高限价。
翻译版: Vegetable sale reduces circulation, can reduce the price of vegetables, at the same time, through the establishment of information platform, direct direct supply of vegetables will also set the ceiling price.
判断依据: 减少了流通环节，降低了蔬菜的价格

文本: 本月12日起，海口市物价部门开始对部分蔬菜进行限价销售。时隔3天后记者走访发现，海口市农贸市场蔬菜供应充分，菜价普遍比限定价格低1毛钱。
翻译版: From December 12, the price department of haikou began to sell some vegetables. After three days of reporters visiting, haikou city farmers market vegetable supply is full, the price of vegetable prices is generally lower than the limit of 1 cent.
判断依据: 限价销售，比限定价格低

文本: 福州10日开始对大白菜、上海青、豆芽菜和空心菜等4种主要蔬菜实施“限价令”。至11日，福州6家主要超市的80家门店全部将菜价调至政府指导价之下，4种大路菜的降价幅度两日间普遍达到15%—50%。
翻译版: Fuzhou began to impose "price restrictions" on four major vegetables, such as cabbage, Shanghai green, bean sprouts and Chinese cabbage, on October 10. On the 11th, 80 stores in six of fuzhou's main supermarkets had the prices to be adjusted to the government's guidance price, and the price cut of four main courses reached 15% to 50% by day.
判断依据: 限价令，降价

文本: 2012年，自治区政府出台《关于加强鲜活农产品流通体系建设实施意见》，提出建立和完善鲜活农产品流通、肉菜应急储备、政策支持、信息服务、质量监管等五大体系，形成以农产品批发市场、标准化菜市场、“菜篮子”平价连锁超市和生鲜超市为流通主渠道，以社区蔬菜直销店、放心肉店、早市为补充的鲜活农产品流通网络。这一举措对农贸市场季节性、阶段性大幅涨价起到明显抑制作用，且促进大中型超市将蔬菜销售联营模式改为自营模式，减少流通环节，降低蔬菜价格。
翻译版: In 2012, the autonomous region government implementation opinion "about strengthening the construction of fresh agricultural products circulation system, and proposes the establishment and improvement of fresh agricultural products circulation, meat dishes, emergency stockpile, policy support, information services, quality supervision and so on five big system, formed by wholesale market for agricultural products, standardized vegetable market," vegetable basket "parity supermarket chains and circulation of fresh supermarket as main channel, with community vegetable stores, rest assured the butcher's, morning market for supplement of fresh agricultural products circulation network. A move to a farmers' market seasonal and periodic sharp price increases have obvious inhibitory effect, and promote the sales of large and medium-sized supermarkets will vegetables associated mode to the self-management model, reduce circulation, reduce the vegetable prices.
判断依据: 流通网络，降低蔬菜价格

文本: 新模式下的蔬菜直营店，价格将比普通菜市场低20%~50%。
翻译版: Under the new mode, the vegetable outlets will be 20%~50% lower than the normal market.
判断依据: 直营店，价格比普通市场价低

文本: 通知提出，鼓励有条件的农贸市场在一定时间、地点开放蔬菜早市，或拿出一定比例的市场摊位免费提供给城郊农民、蔬菜种植户进场直销，以减少中间流通环节，降低蔬菜价格。
翻译版: Notice, encourage conditional farmer's markets open vegetable market in a certain time, place, or a percentage of the market stalls free to suburban farmers, growers in direct marketing, to reduce the middle circulation, to lower the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 减少中间流通环节，降低蔬菜价格

文本: 继续抓好“菜篮子”市场建设，打好流动环节牌。走“政府培育市场，市场引导生产，生产适应市场”的路子，建立以农贸市场为基础、综合批发市场为中心的市场体系，使“菜篮子”生产步入“生产——流通——再生产”的良性循环，不要出现“农民卖菜难、市民买菜贵”的现象。鼓励农产品生产基地、农户实行“农超对接”、“农商对接”和“农区对接”，减少中间环节，降低蔬菜价格，并建立蔬菜订单关系，进而实现商家、农民、消费者共赢，进一步搞活“菜篮子”产品在市场内的流通。
翻译版: Continue to grasp the market construction of "vegetable basket" and play the mobile link. Go "government foster market, the market guide production, production to adapt to the market", established on the basis of the farmer's market, comprehensive wholesale market as the center of the market system, production of "vegetable basket" into the virtuous cycle of "production, circulation, reproduction", do not appear "farmers to sell food, people buy food your" phenomenon. Encouraging agricultural production base, practice the farmers and farmers, agribusiness and docking and docking "agriculture", the decrease of the intermediate links, to lower the price of vegetables, and establish the vegetable order relation, achieving win-win merchants, farmers, consumers, further stimulates circulation within the "vegetable basket" products in the market.
判断依据: 减少中间环节，降低蔬菜价格

文本: 据农业部消息，通过实施稳定菜价的一系列政策措施，“五一”节后，蔬菜价格下滑幅度明显趋缓，个别地区产销矛盾明显缓解。
翻译版: According to the Ministry of Agriculture news, through the implementation of a series of policy measures to stabilize vegetable prices, "51" after the holiday, vegetable prices fell significantly slowed down, individual areas of production and marketing contradictions significantly eased.
判断依据: 稳定菜价、蔬菜价格下滑幅度明显趋缓

文本: 近日，海南省物价局制定下发了《海南省基本蔬菜品种价格区间调控管理办法》，对本地居民经常食用的10种蔬菜的价格调控区间、监测点设置、采价方式以及督导考核等方面进行规定，保证平时价格涨幅不超过目标价格的30%，确保全省菜价稳定。
翻译版: Recently, the Hainan Provincial Price Bureau has issued a "Hainan Province, the basic varieties of vegetable varieties price control management approach", the local residents often eat 10 kinds of vegetables, price control interval, monitoring points set, the way of procurement and supervision and other aspects of supervision Regulations, to ensure that the usual price increase does not exceed 30% of the target price to ensure that the province of vegetable prices stable.
判断依据: 价格调控区间，价格涨幅不超过，菜价稳定

文本: 为应对极端天气影响，保证蔬菜正常供应，市相关部门今年借助南环桥批发市场这一平台实行应急供应双保险制度：建立应急保供制度，该批发市场与48家保供单位基地签订《应急保供协议》，如遭遇极端灾害性天气，市场立即启动应急预案，48家应急保供单位基地从常熟董浜、吴江澄湖等近郊基地优先调运货源，确保每天可供上市蔬菜1340吨。同时启动储备制度，市场强化日常储备工作，特别是针对冬季蔬菜产储特点，启动冷库和应急仓储区冬季蔬菜保供储备，按照耐贮存蔬菜品种5-7天消费量的动态库存，结合本地消费习惯和自身储藏能力适当进行调整，保证在一周内，每天的供应量可达正常水平，确保苏州市场供应货源稳定和价格平稳。
翻译版: In order to cope with the extreme weather, to ensure the normal supply of vegetables, the relevant departments of the city this year with the South Ring Bridge wholesale market this platform to implement emergency supply double insurance system: the establishment of emergency security system, the wholesale market and 48 security units signed a base For the implementation of the agreement, "such as the face of extreme disaster weather, the market immediately start contingency plans, 48 emergency security unit base from Changshu Dong Bang, Wujiang Cheng Lake and other suburban base priority delivery, to ensure that every day for 1340 tons of vegetables listed. At the same time start the reserve system, the market to strengthen the daily reserve work, especially for winter vegetable production and storage characteristics, start cold storage and emergency storage area winter vegetable reserves, according to the storage of vegetable varieties 5-7 days consumption of dynamic inventory, combined with local consumption Habits and their own storage capacity to make appropriate adjustments to ensure that within a week, the daily supply of up to normal levels, to ensure stable supply of Suzhou market supply and stable prices.
判断依据: 保证蔬菜正常供应、建立应急保供制度、价格平稳

文本: 当地政府部门多头分段管理，试图以单点政策、项目撬动菜价系统，但收效甚微。
翻译版: The local government departments long section management, trying to single point of policy, project leveraging vegetable price system, but with little success.
判断依据: 分段管理、收效甚微

文本: 据国家发展和改革委员会17日介绍，发展改革委近日发出紧急通知，要求各地完善促进蔬菜生产和流通的政策，努力降低蔬菜生产经营成本，在稳定蔬菜价格，保护菜农利益的同时，保障城镇居民生活。
翻译版: According to the National Development and Reform Commission on the 17th, the Development and Reform Commission issued an urgent notice recently, requiring all localities to improve the promotion of vegetable production and circulation policy, efforts to reduce the cost of vegetable production and management, in the stability of vegetable prices to protect the interests of farmers at the same time, life.
判断依据: 完善促进蔬菜生产和流通的政策、降低蔬菜生产经营成本、稳定蔬菜价格

文本: “菜篮子”工程的实施有效化解了低温寡照和雨雪冰冻天气的不利影响，确保了春节期间江西蔬菜市场有效供给和价格基本平稳。
翻译版: The implementation of the "vegetable basket" project has effectively solved the adverse effects of low temperature and light rain and freezing rain and snow weather, ensuring the effective supply of vegetables market in Jiangxi Province during the Spring Festival and the price is basically stable.
判断依据: “菜篮子”工程、价格基本平稳

文本: 记者从北京市民政局获悉，民政部门已开始物价监测，当物价上涨达到政策规定的一定标准时，将给本市低保及困难人员发放临时生活补贴，并在必要时考虑提高低保标准。
翻译版: Reporters learned from the Beijing Municipal Civil Affairs Bureau, the civil affairs departments have begun to price monitoring, when prices rose to meet certain standards set by the policy, will give the city subsistence allowances and difficult personnel to pay temporary living allowance, and when necessary to consider raising the minimum standard.
判断依据: 物价监测、生活补贴

文本: 2月10日上午，三亚市政府副市长李劲松带领市发改委(物价局)、市农业局等相关单位对政府惠家菜篮子专营店和“食为鲜”公司仓储库进行调研，了解春节期间基本蔬菜品种应急调运情况以及40个平价网点蔬菜供应及销售情况，并要求相关单位切实做好春节期间保供稳价工作。
翻译版: On the morning of February 10, Li Jinsong, vice mayor of Sanya Municipal Government, led the city development and Reform Commission (Price Bureau), the Municipal Bureau of Agriculture and other relevant units to the government Huijia vegetable basket franchise stores and "fresh food" warehouse research to understand the basic during the Spring Festival Vegetable varieties of emergency transport situation and 40 parity outlets vegetable supply and sales, and asked the relevant units to do a good job during the Spring Festival for the stable price of work.
判断依据: 应急调运情况、保供稳价

文本: 山东启动蔬菜价格保险试点 蔬菜价低了可获赔
翻译版: Shandong start vegetable price insurance pilot vegetable prices can be compensated low
判断依据: 蔬菜价格保险、价低了可获赔

文本: 农业部迅速行动、及时部署，以坚决的态度、有力的措施，全力抓好蔬菜生产，保障市场供应和价格基本稳定。
翻译版: The Ministry of Agriculture prompt action, timely deployment, with a firm attitude, strong measures to take full advantage of vegetable production, protection of market supply and prices are basically stable.
判断依据: 农业部、市场供应、价格基本稳定

文本: “地方政府以‘指导价’来平抑物价是合理的，不仅可以稳定市场蔬菜价格、抑制菜价的快速上涨、保证广大群众吃到平价蔬菜，还能起到监督零售商、有效控制过高的蔬菜批零差价率的作用。”中投顾问食品行业研究员周思然对福州对蔬菜实行最高限价持肯定态度。
翻译版: Local government to 'guide the price' to stabilize prices is reasonable, not only can stabilize the market price of vegetables, inhibit the rapid rise in vegetable prices to ensure that the masses eat cheap vegetables, but also play a supervisory retailer, effective control too high The role of vegetable wholesale and retail price difference. Investment consultants food industry researcher Zhou Siran Fuzhou on the implementation of the maximum price of vegetables with a positive attitude.
判断依据: 指导价、稳定市场蔬菜价格、平价蔬菜

文本: 另外刘通还说北京市发改委和北京市政府也出台了一些政策来保证冬季蔬菜的市场供应。具体情况是这样的，从11月1日起在新发地农产品市场对八类农产品实行减免入场交易费，同时各个区县对其管辖范围内的农产品批发市场也给予适当的优惠，减免进场交易费以降低物流成本，保证菜价的稳定。
翻译版: In addition, Liu also said that the Beijing Municipal Development and Reform Commission and the Beijing Municipal Government has also introduced a number of policies to ensure that the winter vegetable market supply. The specific situation is this, from November 1 on the new agricultural products in the market for the eight categories of agricultural products to implement the transaction fee reduction, while the various districts and counties within the jurisdiction of the agricultural products wholesale market also give appropriate concessions, Field transaction fee to reduce logistics costs, to ensure the stability of vegetable prices.
判断依据: 减免入场交易费、菜价的稳定

文本: 从省商务厅获悉，河北省将于明天至16日（农历腊月十八至廿八），在全省范围内启动肉菜补贴销售工作，以低于市场20%价格补贴销售蔬菜，以每市斤低于市场1元和4元的价格补贴销售猪肉和牛羊肉
翻译版: From the Provincial Department of Commerce was informed that Hebei Province will be tomorrow to 16 (lunar January 18 to 28), in the province to start meat subsidies to sell jobs to 20% below the market price subsidies to sell vegetables to each city Kg less than the market 1 yuan and 4 yuan price subsidies to sell pork and beef and mutton
判断依据: 肉菜补贴销售工作、以低于市场20%价格补贴销售蔬菜

文本: 今年以来，物价部门按照省政府的要求，积极采取有效措施，认真抓好“菜十条”各项工作的落实，全力做好保供稳价工作。
翻译版: This year, the price department in accordance with the requirements of the provincial government, and actively take effective measures to seriously grasp the "food ten" the implementation of the work, to do a good job for the stability of the work.
判断依据: 认真抓好“菜十条”、稳价工作

文本: 厦门实施政府差价补贴销售平价蔬菜的政策也将暂停，此举对市场价格起到了引导示范作用，抑制价格上涨效果明显，政府稳定控价措施得以落实
翻译版: Xiamen to implement the government subsidies to subsidize the sale of cheap vegetable policy will also be suspended, the move on the market price has played a guiding role in guiding the suppression of price increases effect is obvious, the government stable control measures to be implemented
判断依据: 差价补贴、政策也将暂停、稳定控价

文本: 记者昨天从市交通委获悉，为稳定消费价格总水平，本市于11月27日起，提前4天开始执行鲜活农产品绿色通道政策，以降低农副产品运输流通成本。
翻译版: Reporters learned yesterday from the Municipal Transport Committee, in order to stabilize the overall level of consumer prices, the city on November 27, 4 days ahead of the implementation of fresh agricultural products green channel policy to reduce the cost of agricultural and sideline products transport and circulation.
判断依据: 稳定消费价格总水平、农产品绿色通道

文本: 启动价格协商机制，5种蔬菜获政府补贴。为保障市场供应，稳定蔬菜价格，目前福州已启动蔬菜价格协商机制。
翻译版: Start the price negotiation mechanism, five kinds of vegetables received government subsidies. In order to protect the market supply, stable vegetable prices, Fuzhou has started the vegetable price consultation mechanism.
判断依据: 5种蔬菜获政府补贴、稳定蔬菜价格

文本: 眼见着2017年新年春节正缓缓向我们走来，海南省物价局再出“秒杀绝招”——制定《海南省基本蔬菜品种价格区间调控管理办法》(以下简称《管理办法》)确定基本蔬菜品种目标价格，把蔬菜价格涨幅调控在合理的区间。
翻译版: See the 2017 New Year Spring Festival is slowly coming to us, the Hainan Provincial Price Bureau and then "spike trick" - the development of "basic vegetable varieties in Hainan Province price range management approach" (hereinafter referred to as "management approach") to determine the basic vegetables Variety of target prices, the price adjustment of vegetables in a reasonable range.
判断依据: 蔬菜品种价格区间调控、蔬菜价格涨幅调控在合理的区间

文本: 政府要科学选择调控时机，加大农业保险推进力度，把政策性保险延伸到生产、运输、加工、销售等各环节，最大限度地化解风险，保持市场稳定。
翻译版: The government should scientifically choose the timing of regulation and control, increase the intensity of agricultural insurance, extend the policy insurance to production, transportation, processing and sales, and finally resolve the risks and keep the market stable.
判断依据: 农业保险、最大限度地化解风险、保持市场稳定

文本: 当蔬菜价格超过政府调控涨幅时，市县政府通过提高本地蔬菜产能，加大外地蔬菜调运力度，必要时采取限价销售等多种措施，解决基本蔬菜品种涨幅过大和价格过高等突出问题，确保基本蔬菜品种供应和价格水平的稳定。
翻译版: When the price of vegetables over the government control gains, the city and county government by increasing the local vegetable production capacity, increase the field of vegetable control efforts, if necessary, to limit sales and other measures to solve the basic vegetable varieties rose too much and the price is too high and other outstanding issues to ensure Basic vegetable variety supply and price level stability.
判断依据: 当蔬菜价格超过政府调控涨幅时、采取限价销售、价格水平的稳定

文本: 为让广大群众过一个祥和快乐的节日，奇台县政府拿出资金进行羊肉和蔬菜补贴，从9月18日在全县7个政府惠民肉食店和15个政府惠民副食品店敞开供应新鲜羊肉和平价蔬菜。
翻译版: In order to let the masses have a peaceful and happy holiday, Qitai County government to come up with funds for lamb and vegetable subsidies, from September 18 in the county seven government Huimin meat stores and 15 government Huimin non-staple food store open Fresh lamb and cheap vegetables.
判断依据: 蔬菜补贴、平价蔬菜

文本: 日前，我省物价局转发《国家发展改革委关于完善价格政策促进蔬菜生产流通的通知》，同时说明，今年年底前我省将尽快建立我省价格调节基金，充分运用好价格调节基金支持蔬菜的生产和流通。
翻译版: Recently, the Provincial Price Bureau forwarded the "National Development and Reform Commission on the improvement of price policy to promote the circulation of vegetable production notice", also pointed out that by the end of this year before the province will establish our province price adjustment fund, make full use of the price adjustment fund to support vegetables Production and circulation.
判断依据: 价格调节基金、蔬菜的生产和流通

文本: “菜价过高时，可以运用各种措施平抑物价，但菜价大跌时，有效手段却不多。”宁夏物价局综合调控处调研员贺志勤说，宁夏试点蔬菜价格保险，旨在尝试用市场化手段帮助农户提高抗风险能力。
翻译版: Vegetable prices are too high, you can use a variety of measures to stabilize prices, but the vegetable prices fell, the effective means is not much. Ningxia Price Bureau, a comprehensive control researcher He Zhiqin said, Ningxia pilot vegetable price insurance, Market means to help farmers improve their ability to resist risks.
判断依据: 蔬菜价格保险、物价局综合调控处、农户提高抗风险能力

文本: 今年中秋、国庆两节，锦州市拿出200万元，对猪肉、鲜蛋、蔬菜进行价格补贴，让市民吃得安心、满意。这个国庆节，锦州百姓过得乐和。
翻译版: This year the Mid-Autumn Festival, National Day two, Jinzhou City, took out 200 million, pork, eggs, vegetables, price subsidies, so that the public eat peace of mind, satisfaction. This National Day, Jinzhou people had fun and.
判断依据: 蔬菜进行价格补贴、市民吃得安心、满意

文本:
从今年9月份起至明年4月，每月的1日至15日，银川市将在三区对10种蔬菜施行价格临时调控措施。经充分调研和市场摸底，银川市决定选取百姓需求量大、价格高的黄瓜、羊角椒、蒜薹、韭菜、香芹、豆角、西红柿、西兰花、娃娃菜、大葱10种蔬菜作为调控菜。调控期间，在市辖区选取部分大中型超市门店、社区蔬菜直销店、菜篮子连锁超市、标准化菜市场作为政府价格惠民销售点，120天累计将投放7200吨，每位消费者每次购买量不得超过7.5公斤。调控菜指导零售价，原则上执行银川市北环蔬菜果品批发市场前一日批发价，最高不得超过前一日批发价5%

从今年9月份起至明年4月，每月的1日至15日，银川市将在三区对10种蔬菜施行价格临时调控措施。

From September this year to April next year, the monthly 1 to 15, Yinchuan City in the three districts of 10 kinds of vegetables to implement the price of temporary control measures.Through full investigation and market thoroughly, Yinchuan City decided to select the people demand Large and high prices of cucumber, sheep pepper, garlic sprouts, leeks, celery, beans, tomatoes, broccoli, baby food, green onions 10 kinds of vegetables as a control dish during the control period, in the municipal area to select some large and medium supermarket stores, community vegetables Direct sales shop, vegetable basket supermarket chain, the standardization of the market as a government price Huimin point of sale, 120 days will be put 7200 tons, each consumer purchase amount should not exceed 7.5 kg. 文本: 12月28日，记者从海口市菜篮子工程建设第11次联席会议上了解到，2016至2017年冬天易出现冷冬，可能出现拉尼娜现象，造成蔬菜减产。随着2017元旦、春节临近，为避免出现去年春节菜价暴涨情况，海口采取增加批发网点、发挥末端销售网点作用、搭建信息平台等措施，保证“两节”期间蔬菜充足稳价供应。　据了解，为健全蔬菜保供稳价机制，2016年以来，海口市相关部门一直在不断完善蔬菜生产、调运、批发、流通、运输5个环节，确保重大节日蔬菜正常供应。11月海口市菜价排名全国36个大中城市第11名，比去年下降2位，稳定菜价已取得一定成效。
翻译版: On December 28, reporters learned from the 11th joint conference on the construction of a basket project in haikou city that the winter of 2016 to 2017 could be a cold winter, and a la Nina phenomenon could occur, resulting in reduced vegetable production. As New Year's day, Spring Festival of 2017 approaches, to avoid the Spring Festival last year prices soaring, haikou to increase wholesale outlets, play a role of terminal sales outlets, set up information platform, and so on measures to ensure that during the period of "two" vegetable price supply sufficient stability. According to understand, to improve the vegetables for price mechanism, since 2016, the haikou city related department has been constantly improve vegetable production, transportation, wholesale, distribution, transportation five link, ensure the normal supply of major holiday vegetables. In November, haikou ranked 11th among the 36 cities in the country, down 2 places from last year, and the steady price has achieved some success.
判断依据: 完善蔬菜生产、调运、批发、流通、运输5个环节，稳定菜价

翻译版: Xining municipal party committee and municipal government for protection during New Year's day, Spring Festival, the Lantern Festival in 2017 main JingXiCai price stability, meet the requirements of the people demand holiday life, financial subsidies more than tens of millions of yuan, 65 new vegetable parity levels, 185 retail locations to carry out direct subsidies to limit, to the six JingXiCai 5 kinds of aquatic products implementation of direct subsidies to limit, the sales price forecasts the market price low 6 yuan per kg, 10 days of aggregate supply price 1200 tons of vegetables.
判断依据: 补贴千万余元，价格稳定

文本: 国庆黄金周前期，市物价部门联同商务、工商等部门，依法打击哄抬物价、欺行霸市等行为，确保节日蔬菜供应充足，价格平稳。
翻译版: In the early days of the National Day golden week, the municipal price department of the municipal government, together with departments of commerce and industry and commerce, cracked down on the behavior of price gouging and bullying, and ensured the supply of festive vegetables was sufficient and the price was stable.

文本: 7月13日起，为平抑菜价，武汉市农委将在全市150个门店重启蔬菜限价销售。包菜、白萝卜、土豆、冬瓜等4个品种的售价每斤不高于1元，限价期持续10天。
翻译版: Starting from July 13, the agricultural commission of wuhan will restart the sale of vegetable prices in 150 stores across the city. The price of four varieties, including cabbage, white radish, potato and winter melon, is not higher than 1 yuan per catty, and the price limit lasts 10 days.
判断依据: 限价销售，平抑菜价

文本: 在产销衔接方面，农业部门加强蔬菜生产、流通、消费各环节的信息监测，强化对蔬菜生产、市场和价格走势的分析预警，积极引导蔬菜种植户、经营者合理安排生产和经营活动，稳定市场预期，确保蔬菜供应不断档、不脱销。引导大中城市根据本地消费需求，加强与优势产区的协作，建立稳定的供应渠道。落实鲜活农产品运输“绿色通道”政策，提高运输效率，降低运输成本，促进蔬菜快速、有序流通。推动大中城市合理规划布局蔬菜批发市场、农贸市场和社区菜店，积极发展蔬菜电子商务，开展“农超对接”，方便市民购买。
翻译版: In terms of production and the agricultural sector to strengthen every link of vegetable production, circulation and consumption of information monitoring, strengthening of vegetable production, market and price trend analysis of early warning, actively guide vegetable growers, reasonable arrangement of production and management activities, an operator stabilize market expectations, ensuring the supply of vegetables is not short, not out of stock. We will guide large and medium-sized cities to strengthen cooperation with the dominant areas and establish stable supply channels according to local consumption demand. We will implement the "green channel" policy of transporting live agricultural products, improve transport efficiency, reduce transport costs, and promote rapid and orderly flow of vegetables. We will promote the rational planning and distribution of vegetable wholesale markets, farmers' markets and community food stores in large and medium-sized cities, actively develop vegetable e-commerce, and carry out "agricultural superdocking" to facilitate public purchasing.
判断依据: 信息监测,稳定

文本: 海南全面推出“菜十条” 打组合拳降低菜价。尽快安排财政资金进行补贴，加大财政资金对菜价的调节力度。
翻译版: Hainan has launched a comprehensive package of "ten dishes" to reduce vegetable prices. We will arrange financial funds as soon as possible to subsidize the price of vegetable prices.
判断依据: 补贴，降低菜价

文本: 拓展销路。通过供澳合作、“菜篮子工程”、农超对接、互联网销售等途径，推行“订单式蔬菜”模式，确保蔬菜稳定供给，有效拓展销售路径。
翻译版: Expand sales. Through the cooperation between Australia and Australia, the "vegetable basket project", the agricultural superdocking and Internet sales, the "revised vegetable" mode is implemented to ensure the stable supply of vegetables and effectively expand the sales route.
判断依据: 拓展销路，稳定

文本: 海口16项措施稳住“菜篮子”。建立直销渠道，增加蔬菜批发网点，减少流通环节：在秀英、琼山各新建1个公益性临时蔬菜批发市场，3月份前竣工投入使用；积极争取省政府及职能部门支持，集中力量推进大型综合批发市场建设。
翻译版: Haikou 16 measures to stabilize the "vegetable basket". Establishing direct selling channels, increasing the wholesale outlets of vegetables and reducing the circulation: a new public welfare temporary vegetable wholesale market in xiuying and qiongshan, which was completed and put into use by march; Actively enlist the support of provincial government and functional departments to concentrate on the construction of large-scale comprehensive wholesale market.
判断依据: 稳住，减少流通环节

文本: 为保障蔬菜生产和供应，有效遏制物价，稳定海口市蔬菜价格，保证居民日常生活所需，建议政府加大对重要农副产品基地的投入，加强蔬菜产业扶持，对蔬菜产业经营户和菜农要加大物资扶持，给予相应种植补贴。同时，降低农产品批发市场、农贸市场、社区市场摊位费收费标准，并给予租户减免相关税费等优惠政策，对蔬菜品种实施价格补贴，在蔬菜流通过程中收取的其他费用，按照最低收费标准，尽量少收或免收，力争通过降低运输和经营成本降低蔬菜价格。
翻译版: To protect vegetable production and supply, effectively curb prices, stabilize the vegetable prices in haikou city, guarantee the residents' daily life needs, suggested that the government increase spending on important base of agricultural and sideline products, strengthen the vegetable industry support, the vegetable industry enterprises and farmers to increase the material support, give corresponding planting subsidy. At the same time, reduce the wholesale market for agricultural products and farmers' markets, community building standards, and to give the tenant breaks related tax preferential policies, subsidies, the price of vegetable varieties in charge of other vegetables circulation process, according to the minimum charge standard, or free, less as far as possible to by cutting the costs of transportation and management to lower the price of vegetables.
判断依据: 稳定蔬菜价格，补贴

文本: 为确保蔬菜市场价格基本稳定，减轻市民“菜篮子”负担，市物价局决定动用价格调节基金对进入批发市场交易的5个品种每吨定额补贴200元，以吸引货源。
翻译版: In order to ensure the vegetable market prices basically stable, easing the burden on citizens "vegetable basket", the municipal price bureau decided to use the price regulation fund to enter wholesale market transactions of 5 varieties quota subsidies of 200 yuan per ton, in order to attract the supply of goods.
判断依据: 稳定，价格调节基金

文本: 今年我省各级政府投入“真金白银”稳定菜价，保民生。
翻译版: This year, our provincial governments have invested "real gold and silver" to stabilize vegetable prices and ensure people's livelihood.
判断依据: 投入真金白银，稳定菜价

文本: 为缓解蔬菜价格上涨对低收入群体生活带来的影响，三亚市政府常务会今天审议通过《三亚低收入群体蔬菜价格临时补贴方案》（以下简称《方案》），从2016年国际旅游岛建设配套经费中拨付372.6万元，作为低收入群体蔬菜价格临时补贴经费，发放给该市上万名四类低收入群体。
翻译版: To alleviate the effects of vegetable prices for low-income groups living, sanya government Wednesday presided approval today "sanya low-income groups vegetable prices temporary subsidy scheme" (hereinafter referred to as the "scheme"), from the 2016 international tourism island construction of form a complete set of expenses for 3.726 million yuan, as low-income group vegetable prices temporary subsidy funds, to the city of thousands of four types of low-income groups.
判断依据: 缓解价格上涨的影响，补贴经费

文本: 3日从市政府稳定“菜篮子”价格领导小组办公室了解到，为了做好海口市当前蔬菜生产淡季期间蔬菜价格调控，市政府决定对部分蔬菜实行政府补贴，平价销售，每斤均价2.10元，以减轻广大市民经济负担。
翻译版: 3, from the city "vegetable basket" stable prices leading group office, in order to do a good job in haikou city current vegetable production during the off-season vegetables price controls, the city government decided to government subsidies for some vegetables, parity sales, at an average of 2.10 yuan per kilogram, to the general public to reduce the economic burden.
判断依据: 价格调控，补贴，平价销售

文本: 根据近期群众消费特点，加大稳价销售补贴政策，据悉 “两节”期间蔬菜类稳价销售品种补贴幅度由10%增加到20%。
翻译版: According to the recent consumption characteristics of the masses, the subsidy policy for the price of stable price is increased, and the subsidy range for the price of vegetable stabilization in the period of "two festivals" is increased from 10% to 20%.
判断依据: 稳价，补贴

文本: 目前，河北省已进入汛期，为促进蔬菜等农产品价格稳定，防止物价反弹，河北省物价局下发《关于加强汛期蔬菜等农产品价格调控监管工作的通知》。河北“低保”与CPI挂钩，如遇特殊情况，将及时启动联动机制，发放价格临时补贴。
翻译版: At present, in hebei province has entered the flood season, for vegetables and other agricultural products price stability, prevent prices rebound, hebei provincial price bureau issued "about strengthen the regulation of flood season vegetables and other agricultural products price regulation work notice. Hebei "low protection" is linked to the CPI, in case of special circumstances, the linkage mechanism will be activated in a timely manner and the temporary subsidy will be issued.
判断依据: 价格稳定，补贴

文本: 今年，贵阳市物价局在物价总体保持较高位运行下，及时调整价格调节基金使用方向，拨付2134万元价格调节基金用于蔬菜生产补贴，农业部门在获得补贴后推进蔬菜产业发展，确保市民菜篮子供应。目前，上市蔬菜已经超过15万吨，产地批发价格为1.88元／公斤，与去年同期基本持平。
翻译版: This year, the guiyang city price bureau under the overall remain relatively high prices, timely adjustment of price regulation fund use direction and allocated 21.34 million yuan price regulation fund used in vegetable production subsidies, agricultural departments promote the development of vegetable industry after get subsidies, ensuring the supply of citizen vegetable basket. At present, the number of listed vegetables has exceeded 150,000 tons, and the wholesale price is 1.88 yuan/kg, which is basically the same as last year.
判断依据: 补贴，基本持平

文本: 为平抑副食品市场价格，稳定市场，保障供应，张家口市政府决定投入672万元专项资金，用以增加对大白菜、土豆、葱头、胡萝卜、大葱等品种蔬菜和黄豆的市级应急储备，同时定时间、定品种、定门店，对部分蔬菜品种实施补贴限价供应。
翻译版: As the price of deputy food market, stabilize the market and ensure the supply, the government decided to zhangjiakou in 6.72 million yuan of special funds, to increase the cabbage, potato, onion, carrot, green Chinese onion and other varieties of vegetables and soy, the municipal emergency stockpile, fixed time, fixed varieties, set the stores at the same time, the supply part of vegetable varieties in price subsidies.
判断依据: 平抑副食品价格，补贴

文本: 为保障蔬菜生产和供应，有效遏制物价，稳定海口市蔬菜价格，保证居民日常生活所需，政府加大对重要农副产品基地的投入，加强蔬菜产业扶持，对蔬菜产业经营户和菜农要加大物资扶持，给予相应种植补贴，对批发市场、农贸市场实行收费公示制度和明码标价制度，不定期的开展价费行为检查活动，及时查处和严惩有意哄抬菜价的不法经营者，确保市场价格稳定和合理浮动。
翻译版: To protect vegetable production and supply, effectively curb prices, stabilize the vegetable prices in haikou city, guarantee the residents' daily life needs, the government to increase spending on important base of agricultural and sideline products, strengthen the vegetable industry support, the vegetable industry enterprises and farmers to increase the material support, give corresponding planting subsidy, charging to the wholesale market, the farmer's market publicity system and plain code marks a price system, not regular premium behavior inspection activities, promptly investigate and punish unscrupulous operators to bid up prices, to ensure market stability and reasonable price fluctuations.
判断依据: 稳定，扶持，补贴

文本: 我们将政府菜篮子基地的蔬菜由指定的物流配送至菜市场，在菜市场设立基地蔬菜批发专区销售蔬菜，以保证蔬菜供应量和优化流通环节两大措施来稳住菜价。
翻译版: We will government basket base of vegetables by the designated logistics distribution to the vegetable market, set up base in vegetable market vegetables wholesale zone sales, to ensure the supply of vegetables and optimized circulation two measures to hold the price.
判断依据: 优化流通环节，稳住菜价

文本: 为平抑菜价，海口市政府日前明确：将在4个区各建一处小型批发市场，促进产销对接，减少流通环节。
翻译版: In order to calm prices, the government of haikou city has made clear that it will build a small wholesale market in four districts to promote production and sales and reduce circulation.
判断依据: 平抑菜价，减少流通环节

文本: 近日，国家发改委有关人士表示，为控制部分地区蔬菜价格过快上涨，正积极研究落实相关减免流通环节费用，降低流通环节成本等措施。一些地方已开始动用价格调节基金，降低流通环节成本，努力稳定蔬菜价格。
翻译版: Recently, the national development and reform commission officials said that for control of parts of vegetable prices from rising too fast, is actively studying the implementation of the related relief circulation costs, reduce circulation costs and other measures. Some places have started to use price adjustment funds to reduce the cost of circulation and try to stabilize vegetable prices.
判断依据: 降低流通环节成本，稳定菜价

文本: 3月19日，记者从西宁市商务局获悉，西宁市商务局将指导各主要超市与蔬菜批发户建立长期稳定的合作机制，减少流通环节，并联合政府各相关部门加大投放力度、降低成本、限制批零差率，在保障供应的同时稳定物价。
翻译版: On March 19, the reporter learns from xining city business bureau, xining city business bureau will guide the major supermarkets and vegetable wholesale units to establish a long-term and stable cooperation mechanism, reduce the circulation, and the coalition government each related department to put on the dynamics, reduce cost, restrict PiLingCha rate, at the same time in the guarantee the supply of price stability.
判断依据: 减少流通环节，稳定物价

文本: 承德市供销社依托批发市场建立平价蔬菜配送中心，减少了蔬菜流通环节，降低流通成本，保证了直营店蔬菜价格平稳。
翻译版: By relying on the wholesale market, chengde's supply and marketing community has established the center of the affordable vegetable distribution, which reduces the circulation of vegetables and reduces the circulation cost, ensuring the stable prices of vegetables and vegetables.
判断依据: 降低流通环节成本，价格平稳

文本: 从市农委获悉，为平抑我市蔬菜市场价格、保障蔬菜市场供应，前期实施的“一元菜”将持续至8月1日，延长10天，全市150个销售点继续供应4个品种限价菜
翻译版: Learn from city agriculture commission, to ease the our city market of vegetables market price, ensuring the supply of the early stage of the implementation of "one yuan food" will continue to August 1, extended by 10 days, the city's 150 points of sale price continue to supply 4 varieties
判断依据: 平抑价格，限价菜

文本: 为平抑蔬菜市场价格，武汉市“限价销售”的大白菜、白萝卜零售价为不高于1元/斤，土豆、包菜零售价不高于1.5元/斤。
翻译版: In order to calm the market price of vegetables, the retail price of Chinese cabbage and white radish in wuhan city is not higher than 1 yuan per kilogram, and the retail price of potato and package dishes is not higher than 1.5 yuan/kg.
判断依据: 平抑蔬菜市场价格，限价销售

文本: 西宁市政府决定，春节期间对陇椒、韭黄、黄瓜、蒜苔四种蔬菜实施直补限价，保障节日期间主要精细菜供应充足、价格稳定，满足人民群众节日生活需求。
翻译版: Xining city government has decided that during the Spring Festival of gansu pepper, chives, cucumber, garlic moss four vegetables implementation of direct subsidies to limit, security during the festival the main JingXiCai plentiful supply and price stability, meet the demand of people's day life.
判断依据: 直补限价，价格稳定

文本: 12日起海口市政府定点对4种蔬菜实行限价，平抑物价。
翻译版: On December 12, haikou city government fixed price for 4 kinds of vegetables, to suppress prices.
判断依据: 限价，平抑物价

文本: 国务院办公厅近日印《发国内贸易发展“十二五”规划》。《规划》指出要着力建设农产品现代流通体系，积极建设具有公益性质的农产品批发市场，引导各类投资主体投资建设和改造农产品批发市场和农贸市场、社区菜市场等鲜活农产品零售网点支持农产品冷链物流发展，逐步形成全程冷链。在政府和企业的共同努力下，先后在超市设立了“惠民商品专柜”、“平价菜专区”，保证日常所需的农副产品价格不出现较大波动，给百姓带来了实惠。
翻译版: The general office of the state council recently printed the 12th five-year plan for the development of domestic trade. "The plan" pointed out that to focus on building the modern circulation system of agricultural products, actively building has a wholesale market for agricultural products, the public interest to guide all kinds of investment main body construction and retrofit wholesale market for agricultural products and farmers' markets, community vegetable market of fresh farm products such as retail outlets support agricultural cold chain logistics development, gradually formed the entire cold chain. Under the joint efforts of government and enterprise, successively set up shoppe "huimin commodities in the supermarket," parity vegetables zone ", ensure daily price does not appear larger fluctuation of agricultural and sideline products, brought benefits to the people.
判断依据: 现代流通体系，价格不出现较大波动

文本: 下雪天，杭城菜价上涨，但在蔬菜直供销售点，却能买到新鲜的平价菜。杭州市“菜篮子”工程建设领导小组办公室，在市中心设置了15个蔬菜直供销售点。每个直销点都提供了1000斤以上的蔬菜，实行“定点、定价、定时”销售。
翻译版: In the snowy days, the price of vegetables rose in hangzhou, but the vegetables were sold directly for sale, but they were able to buy fresh, inexpensive food. Hangzhou's "vegetable basket" construction leading group office has set up 15 vegetables straight for sale in the city centre. Each outlet provides more than 1000 kg of vegetables, with "fixed point, pricing, timing" sales.
判断依据: 平价菜，定价

文本: 8月18日，记者从海南省物价局获悉，面对近期严峻的防汛形势和恶劣的灾害性天气，各市县价格主管部门要迅速行动起来，积极承担保供稳价安民的责任，加强汛期价格调控监管，促进蔬菜等重要商品价格稳定，切实做好防汛救灾工作。
翻译版: August 18, the reporter learns from the price bureau of hainan province, in the face of the recent severe flood situation and disaster weather, all the cities and counties in price departments should act quickly, shall bear the liability insurance for stabilizing the price of the actively, strengthen the regulation of flood season price controls, promote vegetables and other important commodities price stability, and to do a good job of flood control and disaster relief.
判断依据: 调控监管，价格稳定
